Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.56,0:00:38.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bells will ring at the New York Stock Exchange\N{\rCHT}紐約證券交易所又迎來新的一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,for another day, on this March 18th.\N{\rCHT}今天是3月18日{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.28,0:00:47.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, here we go. Are you listening?\N{\rCHT}好了 開始 你聽到嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.44,0:00:49.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you paying attention out there?\N{\rCHT}你專心聽了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.68,0:00:52.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good. Because it's about to get complicated,\N{\rCHT}很好 因為接下來會很複雜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.60,0:00:55.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,so I'm gonna start out slow and make it nice and simple for you.\N{\rCHT}那麼我就開始慢慢說 好讓你容易聽懂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.44,0:00:59.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't have a clue where your money is.\N{\rCHT}你一點兒都不知道自己的錢在哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.72,0:01:01.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,See, once upon a time,\N{\rCHT}很久很久以前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.16,0:01:04.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you could walk into your bank, and they'd open a vault\N{\rCHT}你可以到銀行去 他們會打開一個保險箱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:06.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and point to a gold brick.\N{\rCHT}給你看一塊金磚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.08,0:01:08.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not anymore.\N{\rCHT}如今不是了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.64,0:01:11.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your money, that thing that you bust your ass for,\N{\rCHT}你的錢 你為之拼命的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.52,0:01:14.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's nothing more than a few photons of energy\N{\rCHT}不過是一些光子能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.16,0:01:17.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,traveling through a massive network of fiber optic cables.\N{\rCHT}在巨大的光纖網路中穿梭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.68,0:01:19.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why'd we do it?\N{\rCHT}為什麼會這樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.00,0:01:22.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We did it to make it go faster.\N{\rCHT}我們如此做是為了速度更快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.68,0:01:25.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because your money better be fast.\N{\rCHT}因為你的錢最好快速移動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.80,0:01:27.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Faster than the other guy's.\N{\rCHT}比別人快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.32,0:01:30.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But if you want faster markets with faster trades,\N{\rCHT}但若你想要更快速的市場 更快速的交易{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.84,0:01:33.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,faster profits, faster everything,\N{\rCHT}快速回報 一切都快速{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.32,0:01:36.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,sometimes you're gonna blow a tire.\N{\rCHT}有時就會爆胎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.20,0:01:38.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And that is exactly what happened yesterday\N{\rCHT}就像昨天東部標準時間下午1點07分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.68,0:01:42.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,at 1:07 p.m., Eastern Standard Time.\N{\rCHT}發生的事情一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.18,0:01:43.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(沃夫佈雷澤 新聞直播間)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.68,0:01:48.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,After heavy after-hours trading, Ibis's stock price took an historic $67...\N{\rCHT}經歷過大量市後交易 埃比斯股票達到歷史新高67美元...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.48,0:01:50.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,run by high-frequency trading pioneer Walt Camby,\N{\rCHT}由高交易率先鋒華特·坎比當家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(埃比斯首席行政長官華特·坎比找藉口)
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.08,0:01:54.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,disclosed that an algorithm managing its portfolio suddenly went haywire.\N{\rCHT}說管理公司投資組合的演算法突然失控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.68,0:01:57.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The trading algorithm seems to have experienced an unexplained anomaly.\N{\rCHT}交易演算法似乎出現無法解釋的不規則計算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.60,0:01:59.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A glitch.\N{\rCHT}故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.12,0:02:02.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shares of Ibis Clear Capital getting killed this morning.\N{\rCHT}埃比斯金融公司股票今天上午大幅下跌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.12,0:02:04.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,net loss of over $800 million.\N{\rCHT}淨損失超過八億美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- It has gone haywire.  - An algorithm...\N{\rCHT}- 已經失控了  - 演算法...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.56,0:02:07.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- glitch...  - ...a glitch...\N{\rCHT}- 故障...  - 故障...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.64,0:02:08.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- glitch!  - A glitch.\N{\rCHT}- 故障  - 是故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.00,0:02:11.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, so Ibis took a beating yesterday,\N{\rCHT}好吧 埃比斯昨天損失慘重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.56,0:02:14.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but if you've been paying attention to me for the past 16 months,\N{\rCHT}但若你在這16個月來一直認真聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.52,0:02:17.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt Camby has made you a lot of money.\N{\rCHT}華特·坎比已經讓你掙了好多錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.38,0:02:19.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(埃比斯)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.84,0:02:22.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But if you were late to the party, I'm not going to sugarcoat it,\N{\rCHT}若你遲到了 我不會說好聽的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.24,0:02:24.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you got your ass smacked yesterday.\N{\rCHT}你昨天狠狠挨了一頓揍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.08,0:02:29.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But this is only the first round. Because this, my friend, is an opportunity.\N{\rCHT}但這僅僅是第一局 因為這是個機會 我們朋友{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.84,0:02:31.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So here's what you're gonna do.\N{\rCHT}所以你該這樣做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:35.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're gonna stop whining, and you're gonna get back in the ring\N{\rCHT}不要再抱怨了 趕快回到賽場上去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.40,0:02:37.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because this stock is coming back.\N{\rCHT}因為股價會回升的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.56,0:02:40.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what that means?\N{\rCHT}知道什麼意思嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:42.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go throw some punches.\N{\rCHT}讓我們來打幾拳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.08,0:02:54.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My money ain't funny and it keep comin' I welcome the money and the cash\N{\rCHT}我的錢不好笑 一直上漲 我歡迎財源滾滾來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.26,0:02:57.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fad(500,0)\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs58\bord0\shad0\fsp5\pos(320,150)\i1}金錢怪獸
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you mean he's ordained?\N{\rCHT}什麼叫他受戒了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.88,0:03:00.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, on a plane, Lee. A plane.\N{\rCHT}不是 是坐飛機 利 飛機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.40,0:03:03.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. That makes more sense.\N{\rCHT}這就說得通了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:05.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait, Walt Camby's on a plane?\N{\rCHT}等等 華特·坎比在飛機上?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can you pick up the pace, please? It's like dealing with my grandmother.\N{\rCHT}麻煩你能跟上我嗎? 好像我在跟老祖母說話似的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:12.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, I'm not having a conversation with you through the goddamn door.\N{\rCHT}拜託 我不想跟你隔著門說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.56,0:03:17.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, I'll leave it open next time.\N{\rCHT}好吧 我下次會開著門{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:21.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait, now, why the hell would Walt cancel? He called me from Geneva yesterday.\N{\rCHT}等等 華特為什麼取消? 他昨天從日內瓦給我打電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.80,0:03:23.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know. He's on a plane.\N{\rCHT}我不知道 他在飛機上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.28,0:03:25.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And how are we just finding out about it now?\N{\rCHT}我們怎麼現在才發現呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.44,0:03:26.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That is a great question.\N{\rCHT}這問題好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:28.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can ask him the next time you talk to him.\N{\rCHT}你下次跟他聊天時可以問他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.40,0:03:31.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Here. First one's a yes. Second one's a no.\N{\rCHT}你看這 第一個填"是" 第二個"否"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.32,0:03:32.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Third one's just a signature.\N{\rCHT}第三個簽字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.08,0:03:34.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ten minutes, Mr. Gates.  - All right.\N{\rCHT}- 還有10分鐘 蓋茲先生  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.84,0:03:36.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Thanks, Gen.  - Yep.\N{\rCHT}- 謝了 吉納  - 不用謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.96,0:03:40.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The fill-in's name is Diane Lester. They're setting up her remote feed now.\N{\rCHT}取代他的是黛安·萊斯特 他們現在正準備她的遠端存取{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.76,0:03:43.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Who the hell is Diane Lester?  - She is the Chief Communications Officer.\N{\rCHT}- 黛安·萊斯特是誰?  - 是首席通訊長官{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.04,0:03:46.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She wrote all the talking points anyway, so should be fine.\N{\rCHT}反正要點都是她寫的 所以應該沒問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When am I getting the revisions for the opening?\N{\rCHT}我什麼能看到開場白修訂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.80,0:03:49.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're making some changes on it. Anybody seen Ron?\N{\rCHT}我們正在做改動 羅恩呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:51.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Might I get those before the show or after the show?\N{\rCHT}節目開始前還是結束後給我?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know the drill. You just point the camera in my direction,\N{\rCHT}你把攝像機對準我就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:54.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and we'll figure it out together.\N{\rCHT}我們會一起解決的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.92,0:03:57.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It always sounds so simple and yet so moronic.\N{\rCHT}總是聽起來很簡單 但實際上很蠢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.60,0:03:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Look out, fellas. Here we come.\N{\rCHT}小心點 夥計們 這邊走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.20,0:04:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Edgar Rosenthal's office called.\N{\rCHT}愛德格羅森塔爾的辦公室打電話來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- He can't make dinner tonight.  - Thank Christ.\N{\rCHT}- 他今晚不能來赴宴了  - 謝天謝地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.84,0:04:05.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dinner at the nursing home with my nan is more exciting than dinner with that guy.\N{\rCHT}就算在養老院跟我奶奶吃飯 都比跟他吃飯好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:08.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is the 7th reschedule. So can I just move it to the TBD list?\N{\rCHT}這是他第七次改時間了 標記為"待定"好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:10.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait a minute, it's the 7th time he's rescheduled on me?\N{\rCHT}等等 他跟我約的時間改了七次?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:11.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, that's correct.\N{\rCHT}對 沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.76,0:04:13.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's ridiculous. I'm calling him on his cell.\N{\rCHT}太荒唐了 我要打他手機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.44,0:04:14.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, his office said that he's in a meeting.\N{\rCHT}他的辦公室說他在開會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.00,0:04:17.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hey, Freddy, nice call on the yen yesterday.  - Eat a dick, Lee.\N{\rCHT}- 弗洛狄 昨天的日元報告不錯  - 去你的 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.76,0:04:21.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, this is Diane Lester.\N{\rCHT}利 這位是黛安·萊斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:23.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Alan, can you bring the boom in for me, please?\N{\rCHT}亞蘭 把話筒送進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.60,0:04:25.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ed! It's Lee Iacocca.\N{\rCHT}埃德 我是利·艾科卡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.80,0:04:27.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, I changed my mind on this whole retirement thing.\N{\rCHT}聽著 關於退休的事 我徹底改變主意了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.92,0:04:30.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turns out I want your job after all.\N{\rCHT}其實我想要你的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.32,0:04:32.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, it's Gates.\N{\rCHT}對 我是蓋茲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.16,0:04:36.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. All right, I'll talk to you later.\N{\rCHT}好吧 回頭再說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.68,0:04:37.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.08,0:04:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So no dinner.\N{\rCHT}那麼沒晚飯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:42.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee. Follow the noise. Diane Lester.\N{\rCHT}利 跟著我 黛安·萊斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.68,0:04:44.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Memo of talking points.  - Hello? Hello?\N{\rCHT}- 採訪要點備忘錄  - 喂? 喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.04,0:04:47.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You guys at Ibis can't do anything right these days, can you?\N{\rCHT}我猜埃比斯最近幹什麼錯什麼 是吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.28,0:04:49.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, I'm really sorry to put you in this situation, Lee.\N{\rCHT}聽著 很抱歉讓你陷入這種境地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.72,0:04:52.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I fit was something we could control, believe me, we would.\N{\rCHT}如果我們能控制 我們會做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.16,0:04:54.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not the enemy here, Diane. I'm friendly fire.\N{\rCHT}我不是敵人 黛安 我是友善且公平的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:56.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We know that. If you read my talking points...\N{\rCHT}我們知道 若你看過我的要點...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.60,0:04:57.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guy's a billionaire. He owns how many jets?\N{\rCHT}他是個億萬富翁 他有多少架私人飛機?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Walt has already addressed the glitch...  - Five minutes!\N{\rCHT}- 我們會處理故障...  - 還有5分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.72,0:05:01.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,'Cause commercial flights, they get delayed,\N{\rCHT}因為商務航班經常晚點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but private ones, they get to do whatever the hell they want.\N{\rCHT}但是私人飛機 想去哪就去哪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.04,0:05:07.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ron! Where's Ron?  - I'm not sure. But here's a list of dinners...\N{\rCHT}- 羅恩 羅恩呢?  - 我不知道 但有晚宴...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.32,0:05:09.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll be with you in less than five, Diane.\N{\rCHT}我們不到5分鐘就會回來 黛安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.84,0:05:12.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at that. I wouldn't invite any of those people to an audit.\N{\rCHT}看看這個 我不會邀請他們任何人參加審計會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.60,0:05:13.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ron!\N{\rCHT}羅恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.72,0:05:16.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ron. There you are. Is that my Canadian commodities data?\N{\rCHT}羅恩 你在這呀 這是我的加拿大貨品資料?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.56,0:05:17.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, yeah. Sorry.\N{\rCHT}對 抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.04,0:05:20.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry, I just ran all the way back from the Village.\N{\rCHT}抱歉 我剛從格林威治跑回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.60,0:05:24.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I had a meeting with Tony Biscano at Licem Pharmaceutical.\N{\rCHT}我跟萊塞製藥廠的托尼·比斯卡諾開了個會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.40,0:05:25.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, I'll be in your ear.\N{\rCHT}利 我跟你用耳麥聯繫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.00,0:05:29.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He gave me this.\N{\rCHT}他給我這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.76,0:05:33.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What is it?  - It's erectile cream.\N{\rCHT}- 這是什麼?  - 是勃起乳液{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.24,0:05:36.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tony Biscano of Licem gave you erectile cream?\N{\rCHT}萊塞製藥廠的托尼·比斯卡諾給你勃起乳液?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:37.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}嗯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.68,0:05:39.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I guess I wasn't aware of the exact nature of your relationship.\N{\rCHT}我想我還真沒意識到 你們是這種關係{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.84,0:05:41.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They've been testing this thing for over a year\N{\rCHT}他們已經做了很多年試驗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:42.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and the approval from the FDA finally came in last night.\N{\rCHT}食品藥品監察局 昨天晚上終於批准了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're sending out a press release...\N{\rCHT}他們會發新聞通告...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.16,0:05:46.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- And it works?  - Apparently, yeah. Pretty damn well.\N{\rCHT}- 有效嗎?  - 當然 很有效{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.44,0:05:48.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Have you tried it?  - I just got it, 30 minutes ago.\N{\rCHT}- 你試過了?  - 剛試過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.24,0:05:50.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What the hell are you waiting for?  - You want me to...\N{\rCHT}- 你還在等什麼?  - 你想我...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.44,0:05:52.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're on in five minutes, aren't we? Put it on!\N{\rCHT}我們還有5分鐘就開播了 快加進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.28,0:05:56.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mr. Gates, you need this. Don't forget your talking points.\N{\rCHT}蓋茲先生 你需要這個 別忘了你的採訪要點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.72,0:05:58.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, yeah. Put it on my desk.\N{\rCHT}好 放到我桌子上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.28,0:06:01.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, where is Diane Lester?\N{\rCHT}好吧 黛安·萊斯特在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.48,0:06:03.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's all checked in on remote six.\N{\rCHT}她在遠端六頻道等著呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.80,0:06:05.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who writes this shit?\N{\rCHT}這破玩意是誰寫的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.28,0:06:07.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Is the graphics package loaded?  - Last one is just coming in.\N{\rCHT}- 圖片都準備好了嗎?  - 最後一張剛弄好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Great.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.20,0:06:13.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We are still working off the rehearsal script for the opening, guys.\N{\rCHT}我們還在修改開場白的彩排稿{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:15.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But he didn't even stick to the rehearsal script at rehearsal.\N{\rCHT}他彩排都不按稿子說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.44,0:06:18.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- So, about dinner... Did you...  - Okay, you wore me down.\N{\rCHT}- 那麼 晚餐的事... 你...  - 好了 我沒耐心了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.12,0:06:19.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry?\N{\rCHT}你說什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.32,0:06:23.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll go to dinner with you. We'll go to Scalinatella's, let's say 9:30?\N{\rCHT}我會跟你吃飯 去薩卡裡娜塔莉吃 9點半行嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.16,0:06:25.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I still have a boyfriend, Lee. Just like I did yesterday.\N{\rCHT}我還有男朋友呢 利 昨天有 今天也有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.12,0:06:27.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, he's still a bartender in Hoboken, like he was yesterday.\N{\rCHT}哦對 他是霍博肯的酒保 昨天是 今天也是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.48,0:06:28.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Will this work, boss?  - This is a stuffed parrot.\N{\rCHT}- 這個行嗎 老闆?  - 這是個鸚鵡標本{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.80,0:06:30.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I said I wanted a live pigeon.\N{\rCHT}我要的是活鴿子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.32,0:06:31.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, God damn it.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 該死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.40,0:06:32.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We don't have a live pigeon.\N{\rCHT}我們沒有活鴿子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.64,0:06:35.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Admit it. You're gonna miss this.  - You can't find a live pigeon?\N{\rCHT}- 承認吧 你會想念這份工作的  - 就找不到活鴿子嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.56,0:06:38.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sure there are plenty of emotionally stunted 7-year-olds\N{\rCHT}我敢肯定街對面有好多情感發育不良的7歲小孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,hosting TV shows across the street. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}在主持電視節目 謝謝啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.28,0:06:43.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Cover yourself... Roll with yourself in breadcrumbs\N{\rCHT}你往自己... 身上撒滿麵包屑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.20,0:06:44.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and bring a fucking bird up here.\N{\rCHT}就能他媽的抓到只活鳥了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.36,0:06:46.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jim, can you punch Diane up on the preview for me, please?\N{\rCHT}吉姆 給我切黛安的預覽畫面好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.68,0:06:47.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sure. There she is.\N{\rCHT}好的 在這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.00,0:06:49.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty? Patty?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂? 帕蒂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.28,0:06:52.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hi, Diane, can you hear me?  - Yes. Yes, I can.\N{\rCHT}- 黛安 能聽到嗎?  - 能聽到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.92,0:06:54.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee has read the talking points, right?\N{\rCHT}利看過要點了吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.00,0:06:56.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I'm in a tough position here,\N{\rCHT}因為我處境很艱難{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.28,0:06:58.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I just want to make sure that he sticks to the script.\N{\rCHT}我想確保他照著稿子來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:02.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He will. You know us, Diane. We don't do "gotcha" journalism here.\N{\rCHT}他會的 你瞭解我們 黛安 我們不會"出其不意"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.52,0:07:04.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hell, we don't do journalism, period.\N{\rCHT}我們不是記者 就這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.24,0:07:06.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Scream one is up.\N{\rCHT}一號尖叫準備完畢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.84,0:07:16.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Check. Check. Check.\N{\rCHT}喂 喂 喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Money... Money... Money Monster.\N{\rCHT}金錢... 金錢... 金錢怪獸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.36,0:07:22.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,About time.\N{\rCHT}時間快到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.08,0:07:25.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, I'm ready.\N{\rCHT}我準備好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.20,0:07:27.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, here's a novel idea.\N{\rCHT}給你個新點子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.20,0:07:30.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How about you just pick up some takeout on your way home.\N{\rCHT}你不如回家路上買個外賣吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.36,0:07:31.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God, stop. I'm getting depressed.\N{\rCHT}天呐 別說了 我都抑鬱了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.00,0:07:34.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get into your most comfortable pair of pajamas.\N{\rCHT}穿上你最舒服的睡褲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.36,0:07:38.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, no, no. This isn't really a Friday night for you, is it? Can't be.\N{\rCHT}不 不 不 對你來說不是個週五晚上吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.64,0:07:40.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Curl right up in front of the TV?\N{\rCHT}蜷縮在電視機前如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.80,0:07:45.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's 'cause the idea of television and pajamas and takeout, good God, it's like...\N{\rCHT}你這個穿睡褲 看電視 吃外賣的主意 我的天呐 就像...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.20,0:07:49.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You get a pool cue, and I want you to sharpen it down to a fine point.\N{\rCHT}拿個撞球杆 我想讓你好好推一杆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.36,0:07:52.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And I want you to shove it straight through my eye.\N{\rCHT}你就在我眼裡推{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.24,0:07:54.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hold on a sec, Lee.  - Right into my brain.\N{\rCHT}- 等一下 利  - 一下推到我的腦子裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.40,0:07:57.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're killing me here, Lenny. Check your mark, please.\N{\rCHT}這不行 蘭尼 請檢查你的位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.16,0:08:01.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what? I drifted and I forgot to lock.\N{\rCHT}你知道嗎? 我移了一下但忘了鎖定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.40,0:08:02.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Balls.\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.88,0:08:03.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's it.\N{\rCHT}這下好多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.00,0:08:07.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I would rather you do that than sitting at home in my underwear\N{\rCHT}我寧願你這樣 也不想穿著內褲坐在家裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.08,0:08:10.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,watching "Suck-My-QVC."\N{\rCHT}看"什麼鬼電視購物"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.68,0:08:29.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at the new guy.\N{\rCHT}來了個新人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.44,0:08:32.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where's Leroy? Finally canned his ass.\N{\rCHT}裡洛伊呢? 他終於被炒魷魚了吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.32,0:08:33.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One minute to air.\N{\rCHT}距直播一分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.44,0:08:34.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One minute. Clear the stage, please.\N{\rCHT}一分鐘 請清場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.08,0:08:36.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, honest answer.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 你老實說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.52,0:08:38.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How many nights a week do you eat dinner in your pajamas?\N{\rCHT}你一周有多少天是穿睡衣吃晚餐的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.76,0:08:41.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Like, on average, over the course of my life? Or just since James left?\N{\rCHT}平均來講 我這一輩子? 還是說詹姆斯之後?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.92,0:08:43.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, listen.\N{\rCHT}聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:46.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I haven't eaten dinner alone since the '90s. That's hand to God.\N{\rCHT}我自從90年代起 就沒自己吃過晚餐 我對天發誓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, that's just awful. That just makes me feel sorry for you.\N{\rCHT}太糟了 我同情你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.56,0:08:50.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why do you feel sorry for me?\N{\rCHT}你為什麼同情我?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.04,0:08:54.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hang on, Patty. Just one second. Ron, you walking hard or what?\N{\rCHT}等等 帕蒂 羅恩 你勃起了還是怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.12,0:08:56.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This stuff is incredible.\N{\rCHT}這玩意難以置信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:59.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm talking zero to 60 in, like, 20 seconds flat.\N{\rCHT}就好像從起步到每小時60公里 只用20秒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.80,0:09:01.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good, so it's a buy, then.\N{\rCHT}好 看來有用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.12,0:09:03.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Put it away and find me a better lead for next week's show.\N{\rCHT}好了 收起來吧 然後給下周的節目找個好點子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:04.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Put it away?\N{\rCHT}收起來?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.72,0:09:05.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Lee, necklace.  - Yeah. Okay. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}- 利 項鍊  - 是啊 好 謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.88,0:09:06.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thirty seconds till air. Thirty seconds.\N{\rCHT}30秒後開始直播 30秒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where's my hat?\N{\rCHT}我的帽子呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.28,0:09:10.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can we turn down the contrast on her a little bit, please?\N{\rCHT}她的畫面對比度調低些好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.76,0:09:11.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sure.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.12,0:09:13.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- How's that?  - That's better. Thank you.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼樣?  - 好多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:14.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Fifteen seconds.  - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 還有15秒  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.04,0:09:17.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Here we go. Good luck, everybody.\N{\rCHT}開始了 祝各位好運{\r}
