Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.78,0:09:36.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(利·蓋茲 金錢怪獸)
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.72,0:09:40.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Here he is, the wizard of Wall Street himself, Lee Gates.\N{\rCHT}有請華爾街魔法師利·蓋茲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.28,0:09:45.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My money ain't funny and it keep comin' I welcome the money and the cash\N{\rCHT}我的錢不好笑 一直上漲 我歡迎財源滾滾來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.68,0:09:49.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My money ain't funny and it keep comin' I welcome the money and the cash\N{\rCHT}我的錢不好笑 一直上漲 我歡迎財源滾滾來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:54.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,At the welcome mat swollen fat In stupid stacks, the cash\N{\rCHT}金銀財寶都滾到門口來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:56.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My money ain't funny and it keep comin'...\N{\rCHT}我的錢不好笑 一直上漲...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.20,0:09:59.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you very much. The name is Lee Gates.\N{\rCHT}非常感謝 我是利·蓋茲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.00,0:10:01.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The show is Money Monster,\N{\rCHT}這裡是《金錢怪獸》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:03.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the day is Friday,\N{\rCHT}今天是星期五{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.12,0:10:06.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and the Dow has dropped a seismic seven points this morning.\N{\rCHT}道鐘斯指數今早下跌七個百分點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.60,0:10:08.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ready scream one.\N{\rCHT}一號尖叫準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.60,0:10:09.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Should you...\N{\rCHT}你是否該...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.48,0:10:13.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ready cheer three.\N{\rCHT}三號歡呼準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.56,0:10:14.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- or should you...  - Roll.\N{\rCHT}- 還是...  - 開始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.80,0:10:17.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And the answer is, who cares about the Dow?\N{\rCHT}答案是 誰在乎道鐘斯指數?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.88,0:10:19.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a measly 30 companies.\N{\rCHT}只不過有30間公司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.44,0:10:21.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So why do you people keep paying attention to it?\N{\rCHT}那麼為什麼大家還這麼關心?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.36,0:10:24.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Probably because our network insists on tracking it.\N{\rCHT}也許是因為我們的網路 堅持要跟蹤它的資訊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.64,0:10:26.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Right here at the bottom of the screen...  - Not sticking to the script.\N{\rCHT}- 就在這個螢幕下方...  - 不跟稿子念{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.08,0:10:28.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in large font all day.\N{\rCHT}全天一排大字{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.56,0:10:30.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Why does he keep talking?  - And why do they do that?\N{\rCHT}- 他怎麼還在說?  - 為何如此?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.24,0:10:31.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sacajawea, Lee.\N{\rCHT}薩卡加維亞 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.88,0:10:34.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because you people keep paying so much attention to it.\N{\rCHT}因為你們一直關注它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.76,0:10:36.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sacajawea.\N{\rCHT}薩卡加維亞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.12,0:10:38.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- And the circle just keeps on turning.  - Shut up.\N{\rCHT}- 所以就一直播  - 閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.92,0:10:40.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:42.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So let's try to ignore it. Let's try to ignore it for one day.\N{\rCHT}所以我們試試忽視它 試試忽視它一天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.84,0:10:47.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One day, and talk about the thing that everybody else is talking about.\N{\rCHT}就一天 我們來說說大家都在說的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.68,0:10:52.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ibis Clear Capital is down another quarter to $8.40,\N{\rCHT}埃比斯金融公司又下跌了0.25 跌至每股8.4美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.28,0:10:54.93,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but rather than grabbing the third rail\N{\rCHT}但不要去摸電線自殺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:10:58.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and losing control of our bowels,\N{\rCHT}而令情況失控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.12,0:11:00.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we here at Money Monster like to go...\N{\rCHT}我們《金錢怪獸》要...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.56,0:11:02.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Straight to the Source!\N{\rCHT}直取問題的源頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.40,0:11:03.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Straight to the source.\N{\rCHT}直取源頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.60,0:11:06.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As it turns out, Walt Camby is 35,000 feet in the air right now,\N{\rCHT}華特·坎比此刻坐飛機在十千米高空{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.08,0:11:09.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but we have somebody far prettier right here at sea level.\N{\rCHT}但我們在地面上找到了另一個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.08,0:11:11.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's his right-hand gal, Diane...\N{\rCHT}他的得力助手 黛安...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.64,0:11:13.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- It's Lester.  - Lester.\N{\rCHT}- 是萊斯特  - 萊斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.28,0:11:15.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is gonna be on the show in a little while to explain\N{\rCHT}將做客本期節目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:17.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,not only what went wrong last week,\N{\rCHT}不僅解釋上周發生的事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.76,0:11:21.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but, more importantly, what they're gonna do to fix it.\N{\rCHT}更重要的是 她將告訴我們如何解決事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.52,0:11:23.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But first, let's talk market Movers and Shakers.\N{\rCHT}但首先 我們來說說 市場上呼風喚雨的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.56,0:11:27.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jim, cue clip package two and three in case he skips one.\N{\rCHT}吉姆 請準備二號和三號片段 以防他跳過一號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.44,0:11:28.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two and three?\N{\rCHT}二號和三號?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.60,0:11:30.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're wondering, "Should I sell? Should I unload?"\N{\rCHT}你還在想 "我該賣出嗎? 該放棄嗎?"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(北部探索呼風喚雨)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.04,0:11:33.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what I'm gonna say to you.\N{\rCHT}你知道我要告訴你什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.28,0:11:34.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Roll balls.\N{\rCHT}放球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.60,0:11:39.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Grow some balls, man! Man up!\N{\rCHT}鼓起勇氣來 做個男子漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.12,0:11:41.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good one.\N{\rCHT}說得好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.28,0:11:44.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Man up! Lenny, let me hear you say it.\N{\rCHT}做個男子漢 蘭尼 我要聽你說一遍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.20,0:11:45.19,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Man up!\N{\rCHT}男子漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.20,0:11:46.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny, let me hear it.\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 說出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.64,0:11:48.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at these numbers. See these?\N{\rCHT}看看這些數字 看見了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.16,0:11:50.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,These are the stock prices over the last three months.\N{\rCHT}這些是過去三個月的股票價格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.28,0:11:51.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,See these drops?\N{\rCHT}看到這些下跌的了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.68,0:11:53.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get used to it. It's just the way the market works these days.\N{\rCHT}習慣了就好 如今的市場就是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.80,0:11:56.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at this. $3.50 here. Almost five bucks there.\N{\rCHT}看看這裡 3.5美金 差不多5美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.52,0:11:58.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you panicked here, you would have sold...\N{\rCHT}你若驚恐 你就會賣出...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.24,0:12:00.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Who's that guy?  - Who's what guy?\N{\rCHT}- 那傢伙是誰?  - 什麼傢伙?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:03.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- you whiners, you chickens.  - Camera 2.\N{\rCHT}- 你們這些牢騷大王 膽小鬼  - 2號機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.96,0:12:05.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what I'm gonna tell you to do.\N{\rCHT}你知道我會對你說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.96,0:12:08.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mark, can you pan over? Do you see that guy?\N{\rCHT}馬克 你能搖過去一點兒嗎? 看得見那個人嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.24,0:12:12.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're talking about 89% return. Even the Teamsters get excited about these numbers.\N{\rCHT}這可是89%回報呀 就連老師們都為此興奮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.64,0:12:15.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Somebody didn't tell me something.\N{\rCHT}某人對我隱瞞了某事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.16,0:12:16.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Looks like a delivery guy.\N{\rCHT}好像是個送貨的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:19.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Say it. I'm not gonna move until you say it.\N{\rCHT}快說 你不說我就不繼續{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.69,0:12:19.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(漢子)
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Balls.  - Balls!\N{\rCHT}- 漢子  - 漢子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.64,0:12:23.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There it is! Just under the wire.\N{\rCHT}對啦 時間正好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.32,0:12:27.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Now, for the rest of you, you know what that means.\N{\rCHT}好啦 你們其他人 知道這是什麼意思了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.76,0:12:32.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's time for today's "Can't Miss Stock Tip of the Millennium."\N{\rCHT}又到了"千禧年股票市場提示"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.68,0:12:34.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's the Stock Tip of the Millennium.\N{\rCHT}千禧年股票市場提示{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.24,0:12:36.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Telecommunications. Forget the top-rated stocks.\N{\rCHT}電訊科技 別管那些排名靠前的股票了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.00,0:12:38.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, here he comes.\N{\rCHT}他來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.76,0:12:42.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, Mark, stay with this guy. I don't know who he is.\N{\rCHT}馬克 你盯住這個人 我不知道他是誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:45.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Alan, there's no chance he's miked, so just boom him in.\N{\rCHT}亞蘭 他身上不可能有麥克風 你用話筒收他的聲音{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.48,0:12:46.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's see what happens.\N{\rCHT}看看怎麼回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.24,0:12:49.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hopefully you've been listening to our little birdy.\N{\rCHT}希望你們都在聽這小鳥說的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.28,0:12:51.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where's that stupid parrot?\N{\rCHT}那個傻鸚鵡呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:52.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got a delivery?\N{\rCHT}送貨嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.52,0:12:56.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't move.\N{\rCHT}別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is this a union thing?\N{\rCHT}這是打彩帶的槍嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:01.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus!\N{\rCHT}天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.20,0:13:03.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Cut the feed.\N{\rCHT}停播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.03,0:13:05.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(財經有線電視 技術故障 請待命)
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.72,0:13:06.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn those cameras back on!\N{\rCHT}別關攝像機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.16,0:13:10.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Turn those cameras back on!  - Jesus Christ!\N{\rCHT}- 把攝像機都打開  - 我的天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.96,0:13:13.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Whoever's in there, turn those cameras back on, right now!\N{\rCHT}裡面的人 快把攝像機打開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.64,0:13:15.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I can't. Once I turn them off...  - You're lying!\N{\rCHT}- 不行 一旦關閉...  - 你撒謊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:17.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn the cameras back on or I'm gonna shoot him in his head!\N{\rCHT}把攝像機打開 不然我朝他的頭開槍了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.96,0:13:19.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn the cameras on, Patty! Turn them on!\N{\rCHT}快開攝像機 帕蒂 快開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:21.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.20,0:13:22.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty!\N{\rCHT}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.28,0:13:23.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, I'm gonna count to three,\N{\rCHT}我數三下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.68,0:13:25.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- then I swear to God...  - Do something!\N{\rCHT}- 我對天發誓  - 做點什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.24,0:13:26.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm pulling this trigger. One...  - Patty!\N{\rCHT}- 我會扣動扳機的  - 帕蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.44,0:13:27.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, what do you want me to do?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.88,0:13:29.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Turn them on, Patty!  - Two...\N{\rCHT}- 開攝像機 帕蒂  - 二...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.48,0:13:30.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Patty!  - Three!\N{\rCHT}- 帕蒂  - 三{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What do you want me to do?  - Put it up.\N{\rCHT}- 怎麼辦?  - 開機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.56,0:13:36.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are we live?\N{\rCHT}是直播嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.36,0:13:39.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, we're live.\N{\rCHT}對 是直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.44,0:13:40.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, turn the cameras off again\N{\rCHT}好 你們再敢關攝像機{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.64,0:13:42.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna shoot him in his head. You hear me?\N{\rCHT}我就斃了他 明白嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.24,0:13:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everybody understands.\N{\rCHT}所有人都明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.40,0:13:44.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Don't try any tricks with the monitors.  - Call security.\N{\rCHT}- 鏡頭都別耍花樣  - 叫保安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.04,0:13:47.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got the whole broadcast here on my phone.\N{\rCHT}我手機上就能看直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.24,0:13:50.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If I see anything other than us, I'm gonna shoot him in his head, all right?\N{\rCHT}要是看不到我們 我就斃了他 知道嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.40,0:13:53.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do you understand me?  - Everybody understands you.\N{\rCHT}- 你們明白嗎?  - 大家都明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.28,0:13:56.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everybody understands. We stay on the air. All right.\N{\rCHT}大家都明白 我們在直播 沒事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.24,0:13:58.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're staying on the air.  - Good.\N{\rCHT}- 我們保持直播  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:00.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.76,0:14:02.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, wait.\N{\rCHT}等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.84,0:14:03.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's not picking up.\N{\rCHT}保安不接電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Pick a box.\N{\rCHT}選個箱子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:07.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you mean?\N{\rCHT}你什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.68,0:14:09.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I said, "Pick a box."  - What happens if I pick the wrong box?\N{\rCHT}- 我說"選個箱子"  - 我若選錯了會怎樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:10.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I said pick one!\N{\rCHT}快選一個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.76,0:14:13.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm not picking a fucking box!  - Did he say "fucking" on air?\N{\rCHT}- 我他媽就不選  - 他直播說"他媽的"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.28,0:14:15.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you fucking kidding? Call fucking security!\N{\rCHT}你他媽開什麼玩笑? 快他媽叫保安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.28,0:14:17.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, there's a guy with a gun in studio 3.\N{\rCHT}3號攝影棚有人持槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.76,0:14:19.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It sounds like a real cute stunt today.\N{\rCHT}好像今天的玩笑特別好玩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.60,0:14:22.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Would you turn on the goddamn TV? It's not a stunt this time.\N{\rCHT}你把電視打開看看行嗎? 這次不是惡作劇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.52,0:14:25.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I need help. Help me, help me.  - Jesus!\N{\rCHT}- 救救我 救命 救命  - 天呐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.40,0:14:27.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stupid son of a bitch.\N{\rCHT}狗娘養的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Pick a goddamn box, Lee. Come on!\N{\rCHT}選個箱子 利 快點兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.80,0:14:33.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Lee.\N{\rCHT}快點兒 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.12,0:14:35.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do it!\N{\rCHT}選呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.28,0:14:39.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's right. Open it up.\N{\rCHT}這就對了 打開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.96,0:14:43.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus Christ.\N{\rCHT}我的天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.48,0:14:44.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, pick it up.\N{\rCHT}拿出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.88,0:14:47.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yep. Take it out.\N{\rCHT}對 拿出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:52.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Now put it on.  - How do I know it won't blow up?\N{\rCHT}- 穿上  - 我怎麼知道這不會爆炸?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.44,0:14:54.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,'Cause I have the detonator. All right?\N{\rCHT}因為引爆器在我這 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.16,0:14:58.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If my thumb comes off this trigger, then we all explode.\N{\rCHT}我的大拇指一抬起來 大家就都炸了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.64,0:15:01.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What if your thumb gets tired?  - You better hope it doesn't.\N{\rCHT}- 你的手指頭累了怎麼辦?  - 最好希望它別累{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.32,0:15:02.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now put it on.\N{\rCHT}穿上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.20,0:15:06.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Quickly!\N{\rCHT}快點兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:14.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Okay, listen up, everybody.  - Put it on.\N{\rCHT}- 好 大家聽好  - 穿上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.08,0:15:19.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you're not manning a camera or a boom, get out right now.\N{\rCHT}除了控制攝像機和話筒的人 其他人馬上離開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.60,0:15:20.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop what you're doing.\N{\rCHT}放下手上的工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.08,0:15:24.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you're not core-one control room, get going.\N{\rCHT}中心控制室以外的人 都離開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.68,0:15:26.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't look up. Just go.\N{\rCHT}別四顧 快走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.00,0:15:28.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right now.\N{\rCHT}現在就走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.84,0:15:35.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Button it up.\N{\rCHT}系上扣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:39.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.64,0:15:43.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sit down.\N{\rCHT}坐下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.68,0:15:49.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Something's wrong.\N{\rCHT}不太對勁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.32,0:15:52.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Oh, my God.  - Breathe, Lee.\N{\rCHT}- 天呐  - 深呼吸 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.92,0:15:54.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I can't catch my breath.\N{\rCHT}我喘不上來氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.48,0:15:57.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just stay calm. Don't panic. You can breathe.\N{\rCHT}保持冷靜 別慌 你能呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.08,0:15:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm having a heart attack.\N{\rCHT}心臟病要犯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.20,0:16:01.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Do I look stupid to you?  - You are not having a heart attack.\N{\rCHT}- 我這樣子是不是特傻?  - 你沒犯心臟病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.64,0:16:03.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Just breathe.  - I can't breathe.\N{\rCHT}- 深呼吸  - 我呼吸不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.20,0:16:05.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Just breathe.  - Oh, God.\N{\rCHT}- 呼吸  - 天呐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:06.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, I'm gonna fucking die.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 我他媽要死了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.80,0:16:08.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- No, you're not.  - You're not gonna die, dipshit. Not yet.\N{\rCHT}- 不會的  - 你還不會死 混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:11.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Fuck you! I'm having a fucking heart attack.  - You're not having a heart attack.\N{\rCHT}- 操 我他媽犯心臟病了  - 你沒犯心臟病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You're having a panic attack.  - How do you know?\N{\rCHT}- 你這是恐慌症  - 你怎麼知道?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:15.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,'Cause it happens to me all the time. Here, drink some water.\N{\rCHT}因為我總犯 給你 喝口水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.48,0:16:17.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's not water.\N{\rCHT}這個不是水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.24,0:16:22.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, I want you to hear my voice. I'm right here.\N{\rCHT}利 我要你聽我說 我就在這{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.08,0:16:24.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just keep breathing.\N{\rCHT}保持呼吸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.64,0:16:31.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shots have been fired at FNN\N{\rCHT}財經有線電視發生槍擊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.64,0:16:33.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- on the set of Money Monster with Lee Gates.  - Bring it here.\N{\rCHT}- 利·蓋茲的《金錢怪獸》的直播現場  - 拿過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.00,0:16:36.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,An intruder found his way into the studio...\N{\rCHT}入侵者進入攝影棚...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.12,0:16:39.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn on FNN, Money Monster. Lee Gates has been taken hostage.\N{\rCHT}快看財經有線電視的《金錢怪獸》 利·蓋茲被綁架了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.32,0:16:42.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shit.\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.60,0:16:44.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Shut those doors!  - Okay. Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 關門  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.76,0:16:46.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I see you.\N{\rCHT}我看見你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:49.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey! Get out of there! Nobody goes in the booth, all right?\N{\rCHT}喂 快離開 別靠近舞臺好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.88,0:16:51.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody's leaving from here on out.\N{\rCHT}任何人都不准離開這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:53.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Anybody tries anything stupid,\N{\rCHT}要是有人耍花招{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.92,0:16:55.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I start shooting.\N{\rCHT}我就開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.76,0:16:57.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right? I'm in charge.\N{\rCHT}聽見了嗎? 我說了算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.56,0:17:02.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You! Stay still. Stop fucking moving.\N{\rCHT}你 別動 你他媽別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.40,0:17:05.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got something I wanna say.\N{\rCHT}我有話想說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.24,0:17:07.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Patty, what do you want me to do?  - Wanna make sure I get time to say it.\N{\rCHT}- 帕蒂 我怎麼辦?  - 我有話要說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.08,0:17:09.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Follow him.\N{\rCHT}拍他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.56,0:17:25.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.88,0:17:28.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want everyone to know something.\N{\rCHT}我想讓大家都知道件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.40,0:17:31.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I might be the one with the gun here,\N{\rCHT}也許拿著槍的是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.80,0:17:34.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but I'm not the real criminal. It's people like these guys!\N{\rCHT}但我不是真正的罪犯 罪犯是像他們這樣的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.04,0:17:38.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're stealing everything from us and they're getting away with it, too.\N{\rCHT}他們從我們口袋裡把錢偷走 還不會獲罪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.48,0:17:40.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody's asking how. Nobody's asking why.\N{\rCHT}沒人問怎麼回事或為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.24,0:17:43.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't steal anything from you.\N{\rCHT}我沒偷你的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Be quiet, Lee.\N{\rCHT}別說話 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.00,0:17:53.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got to open your eyes out there.\N{\rCHT}你們要睜開眼好好看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.40,0:17:56.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not like the government's no help.\N{\rCHT}政府並非沒有用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.72,0:18:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How they just look the other way, since after they're done stealing our money,\N{\rCHT}他們只是用另一種方式看問題 自從他們偷完我們的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.00,0:18:03.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,they barely even have to pay any taxes on it!\N{\rCHT}他們幾乎不用上稅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.40,0:18:07.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm telling you, it's rigged. The whole goddamn thing.\N{\rCHT}我告訴你們 有人操縱 整件事都是被操縱的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.24,0:18:10.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're stealing the country out from under us.\N{\rCHT}他們從我們眼皮底下 偷走了整個國家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.24,0:18:13.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not the Muslims. Not the Chinese. Them.\N{\rCHT}不是穆斯林 不是中國人 是他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.76,0:18:17.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Let me ask you this...  - Shut up, Lee! Shut the fuck up!\N{\rCHT}- 我問你...  - 閉嘴 利 你他媽閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.92,0:18:18.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shut up!\N{\rCHT}閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.08,0:18:21.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I came here to talk! Shut up for two minutes.\N{\rCHT}我是來說話的 你把嘴閉上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Okay.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.76,0:18:25.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus Christ.\N{\rCHT}天呐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:33.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's all fixed.\N{\rCHT}都是定好了的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.88,0:18:39.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They like how the math adds up, so they got to keep rewriting the equation.\N{\rCHT}他們喜歡數字一路加上去 所以他們就改寫了等式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Which means, the one time you finally get a little extra money,\N{\rCHT}也就是說 一旦你終於賺了點兒小錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.24,0:18:44.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you try and be smart about it, you turn on the TV.\N{\rCHT}你努力想明智些 你打開電視{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.44,0:18:48.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's how they fucking take it.\N{\rCHT}他們就他媽拿走啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.64,0:18:51.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They take it so fast they don't even have to explain it!\N{\rCHT}他們手很快 甚至不需要解釋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.12,0:18:53.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They literally own the airwaves.\N{\rCHT}他們真正擁有電波{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.12,0:18:57.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They literally control the information. But not today.\N{\rCHT}他們真正控制資訊 但今天不是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.64,0:19:01.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What does this have to do with me?  - Everything, Lee.\N{\rCHT}- 這跟我有什麼關係?  - 一切都有關係 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.64,0:19:03.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This has everything to do with the both of you.\N{\rCHT}一切跟你們倆都有關係{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:06.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's why I'm here. Don't you understand?\N{\rCHT}所以我才來的 你明白嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.80,0:19:08.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two boxes.\N{\rCHT}兩個箱子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.88,0:19:10.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two assholes.\N{\rCHT}給兩個混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.64,0:19:14.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two?\N{\rCHT}兩個?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.72,0:19:15.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two.\N{\rCHT}兩個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.24,0:19:20.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You didn't just come here for me.\N{\rCHT}你不僅是來找我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is about Ibis.\N{\rCHT}是埃比斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.68,0:19:25.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Goddamn right, this is about Ibis.  - Okay, I get it.\N{\rCHT}- 沒錯 就是埃比斯  - 好 我懂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.08,0:19:27.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn that camera off.\N{\rCHT}把攝像機關了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.40,0:19:28.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Turn the camera off.\N{\rCHT}把攝像機關了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.60,0:19:30.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You lost a lot of money.\N{\rCHT}你損失了好多錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.96,0:19:32.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You went on TV. You said it was safe.\N{\rCHT}你在電視上說那很安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.84,0:19:34.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Four weeks ago. You stood right there.\N{\rCHT}就在四周前 就在這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.60,0:19:38.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is what you did. "Let's get into this."\N{\rCHT}這就是你說的 "我們投錢吧"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.36,0:19:41.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- "Ibis! Safer than a savings account!"  - I didn't say that.\N{\rCHT}- "埃比斯 比儲蓄帳戶還安全"  - 我沒說過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.40,0:19:45.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"Home run after home run... Walt Camby!"\N{\rCHT}"一個本壘打接一個本壘打 華特·坎比"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.24,0:19:47.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I didn't do that!  - Don't fucking lie, Lee! That's what you said.\N{\rCHT}- 我沒說過  - 別他媽撒謊 你就是這麼說的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.48,0:19:50.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I did recommend it, but I never said it was safer than a savings account.\N{\rCHT}我的確推薦過這支股票 但我從沒說過比存錢還安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.20,0:19:51.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to bet? Come on, let's bet.\N{\rCHT}你想打賭嗎? 打個賭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.52,0:19:52.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You said it was safer than my savings account.\N{\rCHT}你說過比存錢還重要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.84,0:19:54.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I would never say it.  - Come on. Let's bet.\N{\rCHT}- 我永遠不會這麼說  - 來吧 打個賭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.04,0:19:57.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,March the 6th, it was Stock Pick of the Millennium. March the 6th.\N{\rCHT}3月6號的 "千禧年股票市場提示"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:20:00.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I make a stock pick every single day. That's a fucking joke.\N{\rCHT}我每天都播出股票提示 只是開個玩笑而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.36,0:20:02.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got the tapes back there, right?\N{\rCHT}你們有錄影吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:03.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fuck off.\N{\rCHT}去你的吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.32,0:20:04.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Find it.\N{\rCHT}找出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.40,0:20:07.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- March the 6th show.  - We do five shows a week.\N{\rCHT}- 3月6號的節目  - 我們每週做五次節目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.56,0:20:08.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Find them!\N{\rCHT}找出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.04,0:20:10.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How many people are inside?\N{\rCHT}裡面有多少人?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.72,0:20:13.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A floor manager, a sound engineer,\N{\rCHT}一個現場經理 一個音效師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.04,0:20:16.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and three cameramen on the main floor.\N{\rCHT}舞臺上三個攝像師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.40,0:20:17.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And the director, Patty Fenn.\N{\rCHT}還有導演帕蒂·芬恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.92,0:20:20.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And five tech guys in the enclosed control room.\N{\rCHT}還有五個技術人員 在封閉控制室裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, ESU will be here momentarily.\N{\rCHT}緊急事件小組馬上就到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.88,0:20:24.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, we're gonna need schematics on the building.\N{\rCHT}我們需要大樓的圖紙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.88,0:20:27.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Catwalks, exits, entrances, the whole shebang.\N{\rCHT}走廊 出口 入口等所有東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.28,0:20:28.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got it.\N{\rCHT}明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.72,0:20:30.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Vasquez?\N{\rCHT}瓦斯凱?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:34.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If that's Semtex, it's enough for a fireball 50-feet from center.\N{\rCHT}森泰克斯炸藥  一旦爆炸將造成半徑15米火球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.16,0:20:35.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got a line to the control room yet?\N{\rCHT}跟控制室通上話了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.24,0:20:39.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Evacuate the rest of the building. Once it's swept, nobody in or out.\N{\rCHT}疏散大樓內所有人員 然後不准再有人出入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.20,0:20:40.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Let's go.\N{\rCHT}快 播出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.00,0:20:42.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shuttle, shuttle, shuttle.\N{\rCHT}快進 快進{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.16,0:20:44.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Diversify, diversify, diversify.\N{\rCHT}多元投資 多元投資{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.12,0:20:46.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Freeze. There it is. Okay, we've got it.\N{\rCHT}停 就這 好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.76,0:20:48.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Roll it, Jim.  - Rolling.\N{\rCHT}- 放出來 吉姆  - 放出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.00,0:20:52.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There it is! That's it. Let's settle this right now.\N{\rCHT}就是這個 就是 現在就一見分曉吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:03.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The name is Lee Gates. The show is Money Monster.\N{\rCHT}我是利·蓋茲 這裡是《金錢怪獸》{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.72,0:21:06.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The day is Friday, March 6th. Let's get right to it.\N{\rCHT}今天是星期五 3月6日 節目現在開始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.64,0:21:08.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's the Stock Tip of the Millennium!\N{\rCHT}千禧年股票市場提示{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.68,0:21:11.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's see what old lucky one-arm has for us today.\N{\rCHT}讓我們來看看 今天的幸運股票是哪一支{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.68,0:21:17.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ibis Clear Capital.\N{\rCHT}埃比斯金融公司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.00,0:21:20.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I know, I've talked this one up before, but what can I tell you?\N{\rCHT}我知道 我以前說過這個 但我能告訴你什麼呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.04,0:21:22.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm in love.\N{\rCHT}我愛上它了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.68,0:21:28.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Ibis's stock since it went public 11 months ago.\N{\rCHT}這是埃比斯股票 發行11月以來的走勢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.20,0:21:31.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at those curves. So voluptuous.\N{\rCHT}看看這個弧度 多麼妖燒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:33.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So full-figured!\N{\rCHT}多麼明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.72,0:21:35.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm genuinely attracted to it.\N{\rCHT}我真的愛上它了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:36.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not sexually so much,\N{\rCHT}不是那麼性感{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.80,0:21:40.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,although after half a dozen vodka tonics I could talk myself into pretty much anything.\N{\rCHT}喝了半打伏特加滋補身子後 我幾乎什麼都信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.16,0:21:44.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No. I am in love with this intellectually.\N{\rCHT}不 我是真的理性地愛上了這支股票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.24,0:21:49.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because Ibis is run by a man named Walt Camby.\N{\rCHT}因為埃比斯的老闆 是個叫華特·坎比的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.52,0:21:52.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt was one of the first guys to tap into the true market potential\N{\rCHT}華特是最早真正利用股市的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.52,0:21:55.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of high-frequency trading.\N{\rCHT}高頻率交易潛力的人之一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.20,0:21:58.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at this. Home run after home run after home run.\N{\rCHT}看看這個 一個本壘打接一個本壘打{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.16,0:22:00.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And now he has finally gone public.\N{\rCHT}如今他終於上市了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:04.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Folks, there isn't a better bet out there. Not bonds, not IRAs,\N{\rCHT}各位 沒有比這更好的投資產品了 不是債券 不是退休存款{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.92,0:22:06.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,not your savings account.\N{\rCHT}不是儲蓄戶口{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.40,0:22:08.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,None of them are as safe as Walt Camby.\N{\rCHT}這些都不如華特·坎比安全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.92,0:22:10.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Cut it, Jim.\N{\rCHT}切掉 吉姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.76,0:22:12.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, put the numbers back up there. Give me another fix.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 把盈利放上來 我要更多確鑿證據{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.80,0:22:14.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Oh, my God, I'm going weak in the knees.\N{\rCHT}拜託 我都站不住了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.76,0:22:16.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I was exaggerating to make a point.  - You lost a bet, Lee.\N{\rCHT}- 我說話比較誇張  - 你賭輸了 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.08,0:22:19.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I made a bad call. How much are you into Ibis for?\N{\rCHT}我的預期錯誤 你買了埃比斯多少?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.96,0:22:21.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sixty grand.\N{\rCHT}六萬美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.24,0:22:23.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sixty grand? This is about sixty grand?\N{\rCHT}六萬美金? 是六萬美金?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.92,0:22:25.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Pocket change to you, right?\N{\rCHT}對你來說不算什麼是吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.80,0:22:27.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, it kind of is. Okay, look.\N{\rCHT}的確是 聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.92,0:22:30.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You give me five minutes, and I can get you 60 grand in cash here,\N{\rCHT}你給我五分鐘 我能給你六萬現金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.60,0:22:31.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I can make you whole.\N{\rCHT}就還清了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.72,0:22:33.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- That won't make me whole.  - All right. What's a number that will?\N{\rCHT}- 還不清  - 好吧 那你要多少?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.60,0:22:36.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,$800 million.\N{\rCHT}八億美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.36,0:22:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's gonna take me a little longer to get $800 million here, pal.\N{\rCHT}弄八億美金可能會花些時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:42.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's how much went fucking poof into thin air, you dumb shit.\N{\rCHT}他們蒸發的錢就是這麼多 你這個蠢蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.60,0:22:45.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So that's what you owe us. 'Cause I'm not the only one watching your show.\N{\rCHT}所以你就欠這麼多 我不是唯一看你節目的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.68,0:22:47.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not the only shareholder who got screwed over here.\N{\rCHT}我不是唯一被套牢的投資者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.80,0:22:49.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're the only shareholder here with a gun.\N{\rCHT}但你是唯一持槍的投資者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.12,0:22:52.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You think you're fucking funny, Lee? Is this funny to you?\N{\rCHT}你覺得自己他媽很好笑 利? 你覺得好笑嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:22:54.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, don't provoke him.\N{\rCHT}利 別激他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.80,0:22:57.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You must think I'm so stupid.\N{\rCHT}你一定覺得我很傻吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.48,0:23:00.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Trying to fucking buy me off.\N{\rCHT}你他媽想拿錢了事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.64,0:23:03.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not stupid, Lee.\N{\rCHT}我不傻 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.08,0:23:11.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I walked in here knowing there was only one way this show was gonna end.\N{\rCHT}我走進來時 就知道這個節目只有一種結束方式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.64,0:23:15.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I came in here knowing I'm not walking out.\N{\rCHT}我進來時就知道我不會走出去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:19.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sit down.\N{\rCHT}坐下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.24,0:23:27.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sit down.\N{\rCHT}坐下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.40,0:23:29.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where the hell is ESU? And where's my negotiator?\N{\rCHT}緊急事件小組呢? 談判專家呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:31.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Negotiator's two minutes out.\N{\rCHT}談判專家兩分鐘到位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.12,0:23:34.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Patty Fenn.  - This is Captain Marcus Powell.\N{\rCHT}- 帕蒂·芬恩  - 我是馬克斯·鮑威爾警監{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.84,0:23:36.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The network confirmed you can stay live on the air.\N{\rCHT}電視公司確認 你們可以繼續直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.88,0:23:37.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just keep stalling him.\N{\rCHT}請繼續拖住他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.96,0:23:39.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you mean "keep stalling"?\N{\rCHT}"拖住"什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.16,0:23:42.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell him to say whatever it is this guy wants to hear until we put a plan in place,\N{\rCHT}讓他說這傢伙想聽的 直到我們準備就緒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.32,0:23:43.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,whatever it takes to keep him from setting off that bomb.\N{\rCHT}無論如何要防止他引爆炸彈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.04,0:23:45.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天呐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.16,0:23:46.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fuck off.\N{\rCHT}操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.68,0:23:48.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee? You have to keep stalling.\N{\rCHT}利? 你要拖住他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.00,0:23:50.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just keep talking to him.\N{\rCHT}繼續跟他說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.84,0:23:54.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're good at that. So just keep talking.\N{\rCHT}這你可最拿手 不停說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.12,0:24:04.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Talk.\N{\rCHT}說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.32,0:24:11.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, I get it. What happened at Ibis is... It's a disaster, there's no other word for it.\N{\rCHT}聽著 我明白 埃比斯的事是個災難 沒有別的形容{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.04,0:24:17.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I can promise you that Walt Camby\N{\rCHT}我可以想你保證 華特·坎比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.64,0:24:20.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,is as sick about this as anybody else.\N{\rCHT}跟所有人一樣難受{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.52,0:24:23.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah? Is that what he told you from his private fucking jet?\N{\rCHT}是嗎? 他在私人飛機上 就是這麼跟你說的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:33.00,0:24:35.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, if anybody is gonna bounce back from it,\N{\rCHT}聽著 股票會回升的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.40,0:24:38.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's Walt and Ibis. This was an isolated incident.\N{\rCHT}是華特和埃比斯 那是孤立意外事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.52,0:24:39.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's this?\N{\rCHT}這是什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.20,0:24:41.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What is this? Who wrote this?\N{\rCHT}這是什麼? 誰寫的?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.36,0:24:44.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Somebody from my office.  - "Diane Lester."\N{\rCHT}- 我的同事  - "黛安·萊斯特"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.56,0:24:49.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You see? This is what I'm talking about. That's your problem.\N{\rCHT}你看? 就是這個 這就是你的問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.96,0:24:52.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You just sit there behind their little fucking desk,\N{\rCHT}他們就坐在他們的破桌子後面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.48,0:24:54.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,like their little fucking puppet, buying into their bullshit,\N{\rCHT}就像他們的小玩偶 他們什麼廢話都信{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.08,0:24:57.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,instead of trying to figure out what really happened.\N{\rCHT}卻不去看看實際怎麼回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.24,0:24:59.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know what happened. It was a computer glitch.\N{\rCHT}你知道怎麼回事 是電腦故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.20,0:25:02.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A glitch! A glitch! It was a fucking glitch! A glitch!\N{\rCHT}故障 故障 是他媽的故障 故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.08,0:25:04.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shut up about the glitch!\N{\rCHT}別再說故障了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.04,0:25:06.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right?\N{\rCHT}行嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.24,0:25:08.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell does that even mean?\N{\rCHT}這詞究竟什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:09.88,0:25:12.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You see, you don't even know. I'm not stupid, Lee. I told you.\N{\rCHT}你看你都不知道 我不傻 利 我說了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:13.24,0:25:15.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People just at home accepting this shit, they're the stupid ones,\N{\rCHT}坐在家裡接受這廢話的人 他們才傻呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.96,0:25:17.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because somehow these clowns\N{\rCHT}因為不知怎的這些小丑們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.60,0:25:20.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lost $800 million overnight.\N{\rCHT}一夜之間損失了八個億{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:20.44,0:25:21.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Overnight.\N{\rCHT}一夜之間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.08,0:25:24.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And nobody's even actually explained how.\N{\rCHT}甚至沒人能解釋怎麼回事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.88,0:25:27.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How is something like that even possible?\N{\rCHT}怎麼竟然會發生這種事呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.92,0:25:29.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How is that even fair?\N{\rCHT}這公平嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:33.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How's that fair?\N{\rCHT}公平嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.12,0:25:36.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not a rhetorical question. I want a fucking answer.\N{\rCHT}不是反問 他媽的回答我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.56,0:25:37.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you want from me, man?\N{\rCHT}你想我怎樣 夥計?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.80,0:25:40.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't run Ibis. I'm just a guy on TV.\N{\rCHT}埃比斯又不是我管 我只是個做電視節目的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.12,0:25:42.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, no. Do not do that, Lee. Do not do that.\N{\rCHT}不 別這麼說 利 別這麼說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.08,0:25:44.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't get to pass the buck today, Lee.\N{\rCHT}你今天不能逃避責任 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.60,0:25:47.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not today. Not with me.\N{\rCHT}今天不行 跟我不行{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:50.60,0:25:52.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, what do we know about him so far?\N{\rCHT}目前我們對他有何瞭解?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.48,0:25:55.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Name's Kyle Budwell. No wants, no warrants, no priors.\N{\rCHT}他叫科爾·巴德維爾 沒有被通緝過 搜查或警告過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.76,0:25:57.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We sent a patrol to his residence to locate family.\N{\rCHT}我們派了一個巡警 去他家確認其家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.96,0:25:59.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They won't find anyone. The guy's a loner.\N{\rCHT}他家什麼人都沒有 是個單身漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.44,0:26:04.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hundred bucks says this poor shithead either lives by himself or with his mother.\N{\rCHT}我賭一百塊錢 這個可憐蟲不是自己住就是跟他媽住{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.44,0:26:06.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The real losers tend to stay home with their mommies.\N{\rCHT}一般社會渣滓都是跟媽媽過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.48,0:26:10.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, hey, do your thing. But watch and see, the guy's a loner.\N{\rCHT}但是 你幹活去吧 小心看著 這個傢伙是個單身漢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.48,0:26:12.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes?\N{\rCHT}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.60,0:26:16.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can you patch this line directly into the studio PA system for us, please, Patty?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 你能將這個電話直接轉入 攝影棚的廣播系統嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.40,0:26:18.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- We have a negotiator here.  - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 談判專家來了  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.68,0:26:22.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Charlie? Patch this line into the PA system, please. Right now.\N{\rCHT}查理? 將電話接入廣播系統 趕快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.88,0:26:26.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's all about... It's high-frequency trading. It can...\N{\rCHT}一切都是高頻率交易的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.16,0:26:28.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let us know when we're on.\N{\rCHT}接好了告訴我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.52,0:26:30.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can he hear me?\N{\rCHT}他聽得到嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:30.68,0:26:34.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Oscar Nelson. I'm a veteran negotiator with the NYPD.\N{\rCHT}我是奧斯卡·尼爾森 紐約警察局的談判專家{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:34.16,0:26:36.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No. I don't want to talk to no cops.\N{\rCHT}我不想跟員警說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.24,0:26:37.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't think of me as a cop.\N{\rCHT}別把我當員警{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.96,0:26:39.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, what'd I just say? No cops!\N{\rCHT}沒聽見我說的嗎? 別叫員警{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.68,0:26:42.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Cut the line! Cut it.\N{\rCHT}切斷 切掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.60,0:26:43.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I can handle it myself.\N{\rCHT}我自己能應付{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.72,0:26:44.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Anybody comes on that mike,\N{\rCHT}再有人用麥克風說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.80,0:26:45.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you gonna put a bullet in his head. You hear me?\N{\rCHT}我就斃了他 明白了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.04,0:26:48.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Cut the line. Cut it.  - Cut the line, Charlie. Right now.\N{\rCHT}- 掛電話  - 掛電話 查理 馬上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:48.32,0:26:50.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not cut this...\N{\rCHT}別掛...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.84,0:26:54.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Two people I came here to talk to. Him and Walt fucking Camby.\N{\rCHT}我來這裡是要找兩個人 他和該死的華特·坎比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.64,0:26:57.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, well, then let's get him Walt fucking Camby already.\N{\rCHT}那就給他該死的華特·坎比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.32,0:26:59.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, so let's get him Walt fucking Camby already.\N{\rCHT}好吧 那就給他該死的華特·坎比{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.16,0:27:01.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. Exactly. Throw him under the bus.\N{\rCHT}沒錯 就這樣 讓他做替罪羊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.20,0:27:04.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, he was supposed to be here today. He didn't show up.\N{\rCHT}他今天該來的 他沒來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.32,0:27:07.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's his company. It's his crash. So let's see what he has to say.\N{\rCHT}那是他的公司 他的錢 所以看看他有什麼話說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.04,0:27:09.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. Yes.\N{\rCHT}好 可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:11.32,0:27:14.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What happened to the Ibis feed?  - I have no idea.\N{\rCHT}- 埃比斯的鏡頭怎麼了?  - 我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:14.72,0:27:15.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God damn it.\N{\rCHT}該死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.92,0:27:16.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, find me Bree.\N{\rCHT}找布瑞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:17.08,0:27:18.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have her call Diane Lester back on the phone.\N{\rCHT}讓她叫黛安·萊斯特回來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.56,0:27:19.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want her back up on that screen.\N{\rCHT}我想讓她回到大螢幕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.00,0:27:23.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And find out everything and anything you can about Ibis Clear Capital.\N{\rCHT}盡可能找到一切關於埃比斯金融公司的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.20,0:27:24.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Got it.  - Yes, what is it?\N{\rCHT}- 明白  - 喂 什麼事?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.72,0:27:27.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want the PA system available in case we need to speak to him again.\N{\rCHT}準備廣播系統 以防萬一我們需要和他對話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.20,0:27:28.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. Because it worked so well the first time.\N{\rCHT}好 因為第一次"很有效"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.56,0:27:30.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, just make sure you answer this phone.\N{\rCHT}聽著 你一定要接電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.48,0:27:33.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll be right downstairs exploring means of extraction.\N{\rCHT}我們就在樓下 正在討論營救方案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.88,0:27:48.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have Patty Fenn from Money Monster on line three.\N{\rCHT}《金錢怪獸》的帕蒂·芬恩在三線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.56,0:27:50.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Marta, when is he landing?\N{\rCHT}瑪塔 飛機幾點降落?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.40,0:27:53.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't even know which plane he's on, so I've no way of tracking him.\N{\rCHT}我不知道他的行程 所以我沒法追蹤他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.24,0:27:55.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He took the G-V to Geneva on Tuesday,\N{\rCHT}他週二乘GV去了日內瓦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.60,0:27:58.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but then he sent that to Hong Kong to pick up Harvey Bergan.\N{\rCHT}但後來他又去香港接哈威伯根{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.28,0:28:02.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Last location I have for the Learjet was Sao Paulo on Monday.\N{\rCHT}我能查到他飛機的最後一站是 週一在聖保羅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.56,0:28:04.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Monday? That's four days ago.\N{\rCHT}週一? 那都四天了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.76,0:28:07.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know how he is with his planes. When he's in the air, he's off the grid.\N{\rCHT}你知道他怎麼用飛機的 他在天上的時候斷絕聯繫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.76,0:28:10.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you telling me that until he lands, whenever the hell that may be, that he's...\N{\rCHT}你是說不到他降落 不管什麼時候 他...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.88,0:28:14.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's completely unreachable. Which makes this one big clusterfuck.\N{\rCHT}就根本找不到他 也就導致這次大災難{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.60,0:28:16.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have Patty Fenn on hold. What should I tell her?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂·芬恩還在等呢 怎麼跟她說?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:16.92,0:28:17.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She'll call back.\N{\rCHT}她會再打的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:18.24,0:28:19.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on.\N{\rCHT}拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.52,0:28:22.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Diane Lester's office is giving me the runaround.\N{\rCHT}黛安·萊斯特的辦公室 給了我行程表{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.28,0:28:23.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, Bree.\N{\rCHT}好 布瑞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.32,0:28:25.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dave, I need an address for Ibis, ASAP.\N{\rCHT}戴夫 儘快給我埃比斯的地址{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.72,0:28:28.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And, Bree, try Dan Issa at the SEC.\N{\rCHT}布瑞 試試給美國證交會的丹·伊薩打電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.28,0:28:30.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They've got to be sniffing around this train wreck already.\N{\rCHT}他們肯定已經開始調查這個爛攤子了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.72,0:28:32.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Keep stalling, Lee. We're on it.\N{\rCHT}繼續拖住他 利 我們在努力了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.60,0:28:36.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny, can you come around on this guy? I'm losing him in a little shadow.\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 你能追住這個傢伙嗎? 他在陰影裡我看不太清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.80,0:28:39.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You kidding me?  - Just move in.\N{\rCHT}- 開玩笑呀你?  - 你就拍吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:44.12,0:28:45.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell are you doing?\N{\rCHT}你在幹嘛?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.80,0:28:47.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Director wanted a better angle on your face.\N{\rCHT}導演說要好好看看你的臉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.00,0:28:49.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's kind of a...\N{\rCHT}有點兒...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.08,0:28:51.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A little shadow.\N{\rCHT}陰影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.04,0:28:53.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"A little shadow"?\N{\rCHT}"有點兒陰影"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.64,0:28:55.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, "A little shadow"?\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 "有點兒陰影"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.32,0:28:58.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He could have killed you much easier off camera, Lee.\N{\rCHT}他在鏡頭外會很輕易殺了你 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.72,0:29:00.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's a reason he's interrupted you on live TV.\N{\rCHT}他在直播現場找你是有原因的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.00,0:29:03.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, give me a break, guy. I'm just trying to do my job.\N{\rCHT}饒了我吧 夥計 我只是在做我該做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.32,0:29:05.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They tell me to move in, I move in.\N{\rCHT}他們告訴我進來 我就進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.48,0:29:09.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, where do you want to go?\N{\rCHT}好吧 你想去哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.68,0:29:11.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, if you went over there, it would be good.\N{\rCHT}你要是去那邊會很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.24,0:29:12.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Here?  - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 這?  - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.84,0:29:16.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,See, I'm directing a show back here, which means you're hosting one up there.\N{\rCHT}你看 我正在導演一場節目 也就是說你在主持這個節目{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:16.80,0:29:18.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So start hosting.\N{\rCHT}所以 開始主持吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.56,0:29:24.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, first things first.\N{\rCHT}好吧 先做緊要的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.52,0:29:27.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's your name?  - Don't worry about my name.\N{\rCHT}- 你叫什麼名字?  - 別管我叫什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:27.88,0:29:28.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're on TV. Trust me.\N{\rCHT}你上電視呢 信我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.96,0:29:31.93,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're gonna know your Little League batting average by the time this is through.\N{\rCHT}他們這會兒工夫早就知道你的底細了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.04,0:29:35.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,His name is Kyle Budwell. The cops already tracked down his info.\N{\rCHT}他叫科爾·巴德維爾 員警已經查到他的資訊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.12,0:29:38.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Doesn't even have to be your real name. Just give me anything I can call you.\N{\rCHT}不用告訴我真名 我只是想稱呼你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.52,0:29:41.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fine. Call me Kyle.\N{\rCHT}好吧 叫我科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.20,0:29:45.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}好的 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.60,0:29:47.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got the address.\N{\rCHT}有地址了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.32,0:29:52.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, that's midtown. Listen, Ibis is ducking our calls.\N{\rCHT}好 在市中心 埃比斯不接我們電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.72,0:29:55.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I say we send somebody there in person instead.\N{\rCHT}我想派個人親自去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:55.68,0:29:58.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- All right.  - Alan, see if you can put a mike on this guy.\N{\rCHT}- 好吧  - 亞蘭 看能不能給這傢伙一個麥克風{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.24,0:30:00.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, talk him through this. I don't want him spooked.\N{\rCHT}利 你跟他說說這事 我不想嚇著他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.80,0:30:02.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Kyle, listen.  - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}- 科爾 聽著  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:02.64,0:30:04.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Alan. He's our sound guy.\N{\rCHT}這是亞蘭 他是管音效的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.48,0:30:07.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He wants to put a microphone on you, so you can... No, it's okay. It's okay.\N{\rCHT}他想給你帶個麥克風 你就能... 沒關係的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:07.72,0:30:09.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want people to be able to hear you, right?\N{\rCHT}你想讓大家都聽見吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.72,0:30:12.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Why, they couldn't hear me before?  - They could... This will be better.\N{\rCHT}- 為什麼 他們之前聽不到嗎?  - 能聽到 但是有話筒好些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.84,0:30:15.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're tracking down Ron now. I'm gonna put him on the air with you.\N{\rCHT}我們正在聯繫羅恩 我會播出他和你的對話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.72,0:30:16.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Kyle.  - Yeah?\N{\rCHT}- 科爾  - 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:16.88,0:30:19.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna send one of my guys over to Ibis's office\N{\rCHT}我會派人去埃比斯的辦公室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.24,0:30:21.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and see if they can get some answers in person.\N{\rCHT}看看他們能否親自得到些答覆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.92,0:30:24.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We've got a producer. This kid's name is Ron.\N{\rCHT}我們有個製片人叫羅恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.16,0:30:26.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where the hell is Ron Sprecher?\N{\rCHT}羅恩·斯普雷徹到底在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.00,0:30:29.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Christ!  - Oh, my God!\N{\rCHT}- 天  - 天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:29.48,0:30:31.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ron! This stuff really works!\N{\rCHT}羅恩 這東西還真有用{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.44,0:30:33.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's the stock trading at?  - $4.25.\N{\rCHT}- 這家公司現在行情如何?  - 每股4.25美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.96,0:30:34.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Christ!\N{\rCHT}天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:35.84,0:30:37.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shit, shit, shit. Shit. My phone.\N{\rCHT}該死 我的電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.72,0:30:41.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- No, it's okay. I need a break, anyway.  - Hold on.\N{\rCHT}- 沒事 反正我需要休息  - 等等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.12,0:30:42.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yeah?  - Hang on, Ron.\N{\rCHT}- 喂?  - 等等 羅恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:43.12,0:30:44.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, Charlie.\N{\rCHT}喂 查理{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.36,0:30:46.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, Ron. I'm gonna put you on the air with Lee.\N{\rCHT}羅恩你好 我會播出你和利的對話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.32,0:30:48.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, you've got Ron. Patching Ron in.\N{\rCHT}利 羅恩接通了 切入羅恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.56,0:30:49.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you mean you're putting me on the air?\N{\rCHT}你說播出是什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:49.68,0:30:50.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're going on the air?\N{\rCHT}你要直播了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.76,0:30:52.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who is that? Where are you?\N{\rCHT}那是誰? 你在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.24,0:30:56.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm in my office with Arlene.\N{\rCHT}我跟愛琳在辦公室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.52,0:30:57.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who'd you just tell my name to?\N{\rCHT}你跟誰說我的名字呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.24,0:30:59.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that Arlene from Product Placement?\N{\rCHT}商品廣告部的愛琳?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.08,0:31:01.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get off my jeans.\N{\rCHT}別踩著我的褲子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:01.36,0:31:03.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I thought you said the building was cleared.\N{\rCHT}你不是說大樓都清空了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.44,0:31:04.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It was. We walked every floor.\N{\rCHT}的確 我們每層都查過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.12,0:31:07.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, what's up, Lee?\N{\rCHT}怎麼回事 利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.12,0:31:09.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, are you coming back?\N{\rCHT}你還回來嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.60,0:31:10.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where are you right now?\N{\rCHT}你現在哪裡?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.00,0:31:14.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've just been going through tapes for tomorrow,\N{\rCHT}我只是在為明天翻看些錄影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.12,0:31:17.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but everything looks good, so I think we should be in good shape, so...\N{\rCHT}但一切正常 我想我們會順利的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.68,0:31:19.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Holy shit! That guy has a gun!\N{\rCHT}靠 那人拿著槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.12,0:31:21.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Imagine my surprise.\N{\rCHT}想想我有多驚訝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.92,0:31:25.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, do us a favor and get your ass down to Ibis Clear Capital,\N{\rCHT}你幫我個忙 去趟埃比斯金融公司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.12,0:31:26.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,would you, please?\N{\rCHT}可以嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:26.56,0:31:27.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.64,0:31:28.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I like when he has the strippers on.\N{\rCHT}我喜歡他的脫衣舞部分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.00,0:31:30.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right. Right. Sure.\N{\rCHT}好 可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:30.32,0:31:32.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Don't be a schmuck, Ron. Get moving.  - Is this for real?\N{\rCHT}- 別這麼笨 羅恩 快去  - 是真的嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:32.48,0:31:33.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, turn it up, will you?\N{\rCHT}開大點兒聲行嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.88,0:31:35.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's a van and a crew waiting downstairs for you.\N{\rCHT}樓下有一輛車和一幫人等著你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.36,0:31:37.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go. Come on. Move. You should be downstairs already. Let's go!\N{\rCHT}快去 快 你早該下樓了 快去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.77,0:31:41.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(首爾)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.75,0:32:07.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(雷克雅維克)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.10,0:32:24.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(約翰尼斯堡)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:34.53,0:32:36.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(南非新聞網)
Dialogue: 0,0:32:38.36,0:32:39.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's taking them so long?\N{\rCHT}怎麼這麼慢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.04,0:32:42.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's midday traffic. What are you gonna do?\N{\rCHT}正午交通高峰 你說怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.20,0:32:43.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got it.\N{\rCHT}明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.36,0:32:46.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So the home address is outdated.\N{\rCHT}他家住址沒更新{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.40,0:32:48.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The family that's in there now bought it six months ago\N{\rCHT}現在住在那裡的人家 是六個月前才買下的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.56,0:32:52.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,from the estate of one Clara Budwell, a 62-years-old deceased woman.\N{\rCHT}以前是巴德維爾的房產 她62歲時過世的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:53.12,0:32:54.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mama's boy. What'd I tell you?\N{\rCHT}跟媽媽住 我說的吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.48,0:32:55.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We tracked down the escrow company.\N{\rCHT}我們查到履約保證公司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.80,0:32:58.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They confirmed all the money from the sale went to her son. Guess how much?\N{\rCHT}他們確認了所有房款都給了她兒子 猜猜有多少?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:58.80,0:32:59.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sixty grand.\N{\rCHT}六萬美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:59.88,0:33:02.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a good thing you didn't bet me, pal, since he fits the profile to a fucking T.\N{\rCHT}幸好你沒跟我下賭 他真是被我說中了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:03.08,0:33:04.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There has to be a current address with the escrow company.\N{\rCHT}履約保證公司 那一定有他現在的住址{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.80,0:33:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Somewhere they sent the check to.\N{\rCHT}他們寄錢的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.92,0:33:07.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- There is, but we need a subpoena to get it.  - Captain.\N{\rCHT}是有 但我們需要傳票才能查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.88,0:33:09.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get somebody down to the courthouse, ASAP.\N{\rCHT}派人馬上去法庭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.72,0:33:11.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Judge Reiner. He'll expedite.\N{\rCHT}萊納法官會加快辦理{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.76,0:33:12.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right.\N{\rCHT}好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:13.40,0:33:15.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We can try to gain access through catwalks here\N{\rCHT}我們能從這邊的走廊進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.40,0:33:19.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(舞臺 控制室)
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.40,0:33:19.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,or a crawlspace here, and get them out through the hatch in the control room here.\N{\rCHT}或者這邊的夾縫 把他們從控制室轉移出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.12,0:33:22.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,First, we save the hostages. Second, we take out the psycho.\N{\rCHT}首先 我們要解救人質 然後 我們要降伏那個瘋子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.00,0:33:25.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, we're here. Just give us a minute to get set up.\N{\rCHT}好 我們到了 給我一分鐘時間準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.00,0:33:27.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- We've got Ron. I'm putting him up.  - Okay, here we go.\N{\rCHT}- 接通羅恩了 我要播出  - 好 可以了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.08,0:33:30.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We've got Ron Sprecher reporting from outside...\N{\rCHT}接通羅恩·斯普雷徹了 他從外面進行報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:30.64,0:33:32.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As if this month couldn't get any worse.\N{\rCHT}這個月一件事比一件事糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.60,0:33:33.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ron, Ron, can you hear us?\N{\rCHT}羅恩 你能聽到我們嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.76,0:33:36.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm here outside Ibis Clear Capital, where their CEO...\N{\rCHT}我現在埃比斯金融公司外 首席執行長官...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:36.80,0:33:39.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Security, there's a man down there with a camera crew.\N{\rCHT}保安 有個人帶著攝製組在外面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.48,0:33:41.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Make sure he doesn't get in the building under any circumstances.\N{\rCHT}確保他無論如何不會進來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:41.84,0:33:43.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What did Teterboro say, Marta?\N{\rCHT}泰特波羅怎麼說的 瑪塔?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:43.60,0:33:46.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I gave them the tail numbers of both of these planes,\N{\rCHT}我把兩架飛機的航線編號都給他們了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.40,0:33:47.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,no communication with either.\N{\rCHT}但都沒有回復{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.48,0:33:51.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, I'm gonna down there and try and buy us some time.\N{\rCHT}好吧 我下樓去 儘量拖延一段時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.52,0:33:53.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, obviously, this guy just wants some answers.\N{\rCHT}我是說 顯然這個傢伙只是想要個答覆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.56,0:33:54.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So do we.\N{\rCHT}我們也想要答覆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.60,0:33:57.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If we knew how we lost $800 million, we wouldn't have lost $800 million.\N{\rCHT}若我們知道是怎麼賠了八億 我們當初就不會賠了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.00,0:34:00.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I get that, Avery, but we still have to say something.\N{\rCHT}我知道 艾弗裡 但我們仍舊總得說些什麼呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.76,0:34:03.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. You know Walt. He's an open book. I know if he was here...\N{\rCHT}拜託 你知道華特的 他開誠佈公 他若在這...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.40,0:34:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But he's not here, Diane. He's not here.\N{\rCHT}但他不在 黛安 他不在這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.60,0:34:08.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, we can't just lock ourselves away here and do nothing and hope it disappears.\N{\rCHT}好吧 我們不能把自己封閉起來 什麼都不做就想事情化解{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:09.08,0:34:10.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We are a publicly-traded company.\N{\rCHT}我們是上市公司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.40,0:34:12.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We've got shareholders. We've got a board of directors\N{\rCHT}我們有投資人 董事會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.44,0:34:15.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and we've got a CEO, even though we don't know where he is right now.\N{\rCHT}還有個行政長官 雖然不知道他現在哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:15.92,0:34:17.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, look, I'm happy to have this conversation again\N{\rCHT}聽著 我願意對話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.80,0:34:20.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,when Walt lands, but until then, it's not our call to make.\N{\rCHT}但要等華特降落 在那之前不是我們的責任{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.36,0:34:32.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, he's got the stage all locked up. These are the exits, front and rear.\N{\rCHT}他把整個舞臺都鎖起來了 有出口 正面和背面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.24,0:34:33.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, the problem is,\N{\rCHT}現在問題是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:33.48,0:34:36.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,this guy's got complete range of vision throughout the entire studio.\N{\rCHT}這個傢伙能看到整個舞臺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.48,0:34:39.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So our only chance for a clean shot\N{\rCHT}我們準確射擊的唯一機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.16,0:34:40.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,is from these catwalks above the stage.\N{\rCHT}是從舞臺上的走廊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.96,0:34:42.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're putting a man in position there as we speak.\N{\rCHT}我們一邊說話 一邊在那裡安排人手了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.00,0:34:44.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about the bomb?\N{\rCHT}炸彈呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.16,0:34:46.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is definitely a dead man's switch here in his hand,\N{\rCHT}他手裡掌握著生死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.52,0:34:48.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,which means, if you take him out without disarming the bomb first...\N{\rCHT}也就是說 若不能先讓他接觸引爆...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.00,0:34:52.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got the warrant, got an address. Sending a patrol there now.\N{\rCHT}我們有搜查令和地址了 現在正派人過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.24,0:34:53.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Great.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.36,0:34:55.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You see this bulge right here? That's the wireless receiver.\N{\rCHT}看到這個突起物了嗎? 這就是接受器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.68,0:34:57.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, Captain, if we can destroy that,\N{\rCHT}若我們能破壞這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.16,0:34:59.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,then the dead man's switch is just another fucking switch.\N{\rCHT}他手裡的人命開關就失靈了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.76,0:35:02.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Except, in order to destroy it, we got to what, shoot Gates?\N{\rCHT}為了破壞開關 我們要對蓋茲開槍嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.84,0:35:04.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's where this guy slipped up.\N{\rCHT}這是他不小心的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.52,0:35:05.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If he wanted to ensure a kill shot,\N{\rCHT}如果他想致其死地{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.84,0:35:08.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,he should've put the receiver here, right over the poor bastard's heart.\N{\rCHT}他就應該把接收器放在這 這個倒楣蛋的心臟前面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.04,0:35:11.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But instead, he put it down here next to his left kidney.\N{\rCHT}但他沒有 他放在靠近左腎這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.88,0:35:15.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If the bullet's on target, we get to him quick enough to avoid too much blood loss,\N{\rCHT}若子彈射中了 我們就快速營救避免失血過多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.52,0:35:17.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,there's a good chance, Captain, he could survive it.\N{\rCHT}這是個好機會 警監{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.36,0:35:18.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.56,0:35:20.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you proposing we shoot the star of a TV show\N{\rCHT}你建議我們朝電視明星射擊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.96,0:35:23.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,live, on air, in front of millions of people?\N{\rCHT}當著數百萬人的面現場直播?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.52,0:35:25.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.88,0:35:28.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I need you to talk to somebody from Ibis Clear Capital.\N{\rCHT}我要你跟埃比斯金融公司的某人說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.40,0:35:29.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I need to talk... You wanna touch me?\N{\rCHT}我需要對話... 你想碰我?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.92,0:35:32.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Don't put your hands on me.  - Andre? It's okay.\N{\rCHT}- 你別碰我  - 安德列? 可以了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:32.32,0:35:34.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's, that's...  - Diane Lester. I'll be happy to talk to you.\N{\rCHT}- 那是...  - 黛安·萊斯特 我願意跟你對話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.04,0:35:36.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you have an earpiece so I can hear everyone?\N{\rCHT}有耳機嗎? 我想聽大家說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.72,0:35:37.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yes. Yeah.  - Okay, good.\N{\rCHT}- 有  - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.88,0:35:38.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Come on.  - All right.\N{\rCHT}- 拜託  - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.08,0:35:42.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're gonna talk to Diane Lester. She's the PR lady. She's the...\N{\rCHT}我們要跟黛安·萊斯特說話 她是做公關的 她是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:42.76,0:35:43.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,CCO.\N{\rCHT}首席通訊長官{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.84,0:35:46.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Chief Communications Officer at Ibis. Diane?\N{\rCHT}埃比斯的首席通訊長官黛安?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.88,0:35:50.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, get ready to put her on screen two. We're gonna put her on screen two.\N{\rCHT}好的 準備讓她出現在二號螢幕 我們用二號螢幕播出她的畫面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:50.12,0:35:51.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're ready when you are.\N{\rCHT}你準備好了就開始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.28,0:35:52.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And go, Jim.\N{\rCHT}開始 吉姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.04,0:35:54.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Here she comes.  - All right.\N{\rCHT}她來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.44,0:35:58.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,First, let me start off by saying\N{\rCHT}首先 我想說的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.12,0:36:00.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,on behalf of everyone here at Ibis,\N{\rCHT}我代表埃比斯所有人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.84,0:36:04.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we are prepared to do whatever we can to get you to put down that gun, Mr. Budwell.\N{\rCHT}我們願意盡我們所能 讓你放下那把槍 巴德維爾先生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.80,0:36:06.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, I understand that you've offered to compensate him\N{\rCHT}我知道你已經提出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:06.68,0:36:08.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,for his losses personally, Lee.\N{\rCHT}願意個人出資賠償他 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.60,0:36:12.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, we are absolutely willing to do the same if it helps put an end to all this.\N{\rCHT}我們絕對也願意如此做 只要能幫助結束這一切{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:12.48,0:36:15.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, you walk away now, double your money.\N{\rCHT}好了嗎 你現在走就可以拿雙份錢了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.96,0:36:17.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She knows my last name.\N{\rCHT}她知道我的姓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.80,0:36:21.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everybody in the five boroughs knows your last name by now, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}所有五大行政區的人 都知道你姓什麼了 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:23.68,0:36:25.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, it's too late for your money, lady.\N{\rCHT}不 你現在給錢太遲了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.64,0:36:28.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All I want from you is an answer. I just wanna know what really happened?\N{\rCHT}我只是想要個說法 我只想知道到底發生了什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:28.56,0:36:30.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goddamn it!\N{\rCHT}該死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.16,0:36:32.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, the truth is\N{\rCHT}事實是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.48,0:36:36.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we don't know.\N{\rCHT}我們不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.28,0:36:39.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We don't know why the algo suddenly went haywire.\N{\rCHT}我們不知道為什麼演算法突然失控{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.96,0:36:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And we don't know why the fail-safes built to prevent...\N{\rCHT}我們也不知道為什麼 為此設立的故障保險...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.40,0:36:46.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God, I really hope she has more to say than "We don't know."\N{\rCHT}天呀 我真希望她不只會說"不知道"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.28,0:36:48.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We just don't know.\N{\rCHT}我們真的不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.92,0:36:51.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you kidding? This is all she's got? Are you kidding me?\N{\rCHT}你開玩笑呀? 她沒別的話說了? 你開什麼玩笑?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.84,0:36:53.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sacajawea.\N{\rCHT}薩卡加維亞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.00,0:36:56.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fine.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.28,0:36:59.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you watching this? This is getting out of control.\N{\rCHT}你在看嗎? 都失控了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.32,0:37:01.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The amount of scrutiny we're gonna get after this idiot blows himself up\N{\rCHT}等這個白癡把他自己炸了之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.88,0:37:03.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,is going to be unbelievable.\N{\rCHT}我們會面臨難以想像的調查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.80,0:37:06.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You thought it was bad before? It's about to get 100 times more intense.\N{\rCHT}你以為以前很糟? 會比這難處理一百倍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.72,0:37:10.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, don't worry, okay? We can handle it. Gates is an idiot.\N{\rCHT}別擔心好嗎? 我們能處理 蓋茲是個白癡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.31,0:37:10.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(華特·坎比)
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.32,0:37:13.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just stay the course, okay? I'm working Mambo night and day.\N{\rCHT}保持現狀好嗎? 我夜以繼日地處理曼博呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.64,0:37:16.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I would like to point out that this affected all of us.\N{\rCHT}我想指出的是 這次事件影響到我們所有人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.24,0:37:20.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All our board, our managers, including myself.\N{\rCHT}所有董事 經理 包括我自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:20.12,0:37:22.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Our pensions were depleted overnight.\N{\rCHT}我們的養老金一夜之間就沒有了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.96,0:37:25.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Diane.  - Our savings gutted just like yours.\N{\rCHT}- 黛安  - 我們的存款跟你的一樣沒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.52,0:37:26.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait. Wait. I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}等等 抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.84,0:37:28.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you trying to make me feel sorry for you?\N{\rCHT}你是在博取同情嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.32,0:37:30.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that really what's happening right now?\N{\rCHT}是不是這樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.48,0:37:32.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- No, I just...  - That's exactly what's happening.\N{\rCHT}- 不 我只是...  - 就是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.36,0:37:33.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I understand you want specifics.\N{\rCHT}我明白你想要細節{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.48,0:37:36.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. So why doesn't she give him some specifics?\N{\rCHT}為什麼她就是不給他細節呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:36.64,0:37:39.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We know this was a completely isolated incident.\N{\rCHT}我們知道這次是一個絕對孤立事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.20,0:37:40.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's what we call a black swan.\N{\rCHT}我們稱之為黑天鵝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.48,0:37:44.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's impossible to predict, but it's impossible to replicate.\N{\rCHT}無法預期 也無法複製{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:44.24,0:37:45.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"Black swan"?\N{\rCHT}"黑天鵝"?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.88,0:37:46.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's her memo.\N{\rCHT}是她的備忘錄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.04,0:37:48.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's reading from her memo.\N{\rCHT}她在念備忘錄{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.72,0:37:51.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Diane. Diane. We both read your talking points.\N{\rCHT}黛安 黛安 我們都看過你的對話要點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.84,0:37:55.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He doesn't want some PR spin about what's gonna go right next year.\N{\rCHT}他不想要什麼公關斡旋 談明年會發生什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.56,0:37:58.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He wants an explanation for what went wrong last week.\N{\rCHT}他只想知道上周發生了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.52,0:37:59.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.80,0:38:03.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right, I understand. And we believe in complete transparency.\N{\rCHT}好 我明白 我們相信徹底公開化{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.40,0:38:04.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's why we disclosed...\N{\rCHT}因此我們才公開了...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.92,0:38:06.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where are your quants, Diane? Where are your quants?\N{\rCHT}定量分析師們呢 黛安? 分析師們呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:10.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- That's good. Go with that. Get an answer.  - I'm sorry?\N{\rCHT}- 很好 就這樣 讓她回答  - 你說什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.20,0:38:11.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yeah.  - The quants you used.\N{\rCHT}- 是啊  - 你用的那些定量分析師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.36,0:38:13.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The guy who actually designed the algorithm that crashed.\N{\rCHT}那個實際設計了這個失敗演算法的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.08,0:38:16.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where is he? Is he in that building right there behind you?\N{\rCHT}他在哪裡? 在你身後那個大樓嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:17.00,0:38:18.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,'Cause I think I'd like to ask him a few questions.\N{\rCHT}因為我想問他幾個問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.80,0:38:21.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, these are our administrative offices. Our quants aren't...\N{\rCHT}不在 這裡是我們的行政大樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.56,0:38:23.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, then where is he? Is he in Mumbai?\N{\rCHT}那他在哪? 在孟買?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:23.76,0:38:25.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Russia? Yeah, he's in Russia. They're all in Russia.\N{\rCHT}俄羅斯? 對 他在俄國 他們都在俄國{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.04,0:38:26.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not sure.\N{\rCHT}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.08,0:38:29.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But if you'd like to talk to someone, then I can make that happen.\N{\rCHT}但你若想找人對話 我可以幫你聯繫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.36,0:38:32.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I don't want to talk to some low-level schlub, God damn it.\N{\rCHT}我不想跟什麼低水準的廢物說話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.64,0:38:34.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want an explanation from you!\N{\rCHT}我要你解釋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.40,0:38:37.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And if you can't give me one, then I want to talk to Walt Camby.\N{\rCHT}你若不能解釋 那就讓華特·坎比跟我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:37.64,0:38:38.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, I'm sorry,\N{\rCHT}不 抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.92,0:38:40.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- but Walt is on a plane right now.  - God damn...\N{\rCHT}- 但華特正在飛機上  - 該死的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.56,0:38:44.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shit-fucking assholes.\N{\rCHT}這他媽混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:44.56,0:38:48.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm getting so tired of this same old bullshit over and over again, Lee.\N{\rCHT}我受夠了這些不斷重複的廢話 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.28,0:38:49.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Wait.  - Don't tell me to wait!\N{\rCHT}- 等等  - 別叫我等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.04,0:38:50.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What happened?\N{\rCHT}發生了什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.08,0:38:53.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He just shot out your monitor on the stage\N{\rCHT}他在臺上對著你的螢幕發脾氣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.12,0:38:55.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because you're giving him the same corporate bullshit!\N{\rCHT}因為你說的都是些公司廢話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.68,0:38:56.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not.\N{\rCHT}不是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.92,0:38:59.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You have to understand how delicate of a situation this is.\N{\rCHT}你要理解現在的情況有多敏感{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.12,0:39:02.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sitting 80-feet from a bomb! Don't talk to me about delicate situations!\N{\rCHT}我25米外就是個炸彈 別跟我說什麼敏感情況{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.68,0:39:05.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You have got to wake up and do the math here,\N{\rCHT}你要清醒一下 現在趕快想辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.28,0:39:07.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because it is not adding up to me, either.\N{\rCHT}因為我也沒有辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.24,0:39:08.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why is that so goddamn hard?\N{\rCHT}為什麼這麼難?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.68,0:39:10.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry, what do you mean?\N{\rCHT}你是什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:11.08,0:39:13.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, you better ask some real questions\N{\rCHT}我是說 你最好問些實際問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.92,0:39:16.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and get some real answers, and hurry the fuck up!\N{\rCHT}然後做實質性回答 而且要他媽快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.12,0:39:17.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want what happened to make sense!\N{\rCHT}我就想要個說法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:17.72,0:39:20.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not talk to him like that. Do not tell him things.\N{\rCHT}別這樣跟他說話 別指揮他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.84,0:39:22.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Right now!  - Don't do anything stupid.\N{\rCHT}- 快點兒  - 別耍花招{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.08,0:39:24.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let me get you some answers.\N{\rCHT}我來要答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.20,0:39:25.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You need to bargain for more time. All right?\N{\rCHT}你要跟他爭取時間 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.00,0:39:27.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Trade something.  - Give me 10 more minutes.\N{\rCHT}- 做些交易什麼的  - 再給我10秒鐘時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.24,0:39:28.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bargain with him.\N{\rCHT}跟他討價還價{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.92,0:39:30.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle, look.\N{\rCHT}科爾 你聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.72,0:39:33.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You give me something, I give you something. Okay?\N{\rCHT}你給我些東西 我就給你些東西 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.12,0:39:35.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's how this works.\N{\rCHT}要這樣做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.40,0:39:39.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You do something for me, I do something for you.\N{\rCHT}你為我做事 我就為你做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.00,0:39:41.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on.\N{\rCHT}拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.32,0:39:43.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Give me a chance.\N{\rCHT}給我個機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.76,0:39:46.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let me figure this out.\N{\rCHT}讓我想個辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.08,0:39:51.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Fine, you got 10 minutes.  - Okay. All right.\N{\rCHT}- 好 給你10分鐘  - 好 可以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.47,0:39:58.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(紐約警察局 緊急事件小組)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.12,0:40:05.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now what?\N{\rCHT}現在怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.65,0:40:11.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(利: 十分鐘內找到那個該死的分析師)
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.60,0:40:20.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I made myself extraordinarily clear that you were not to go on camera.\N{\rCHT}我說得很清楚 你不能去面對鏡頭{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.08,0:40:23.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am curious. Who actually did design that algo?\N{\rCHT}我也很好奇 到底是誰設計的演算法?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.52,0:40:24.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't we call him together?\N{\rCHT}為什麼不一起給他打電話?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:25.08,0:40:27.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, you listen to me, Diane. You're a CCO.\N{\rCHT}你聽我說 黛安 你是首席通訊長官{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.12,0:40:29.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And that is all you are and that is nothing.\N{\rCHT}僅此而已 一文不值{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.44,0:40:30.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've seen a dozen girls like you come and go.\N{\rCHT}我見過好多你這樣的姑娘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.76,0:40:31.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Really? Girls like me?  - Yeah!\N{\rCHT}- 真的? 我這樣的?  - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.92,0:40:32.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't have to stand here and listen to this.\N{\rCHT}我沒必要站在這裡聽這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:33.08,0:40:36.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Well, you're fired, Diane!  - You can't fire me. I don't report to you.\N{\rCHT}- 你被解雇了 黛安  - 你不能解雇我 你不是我上司{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.36,0:40:39.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's not our job to bail out this psychopath! Do not walk away from me!\N{\rCHT}解救這個瘋子不是我們的責任 別就這麼走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.60,0:40:41.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't report to you, Avery.\N{\rCHT}你不是我的上司 艾弗裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.52,0:40:45.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ryan, get me a list of every quant that's been on our payroll since we went public.\N{\rCHT}瑞恩 給我自從上市以來 所有我們雇用的定量分析師名單{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.60,0:40:48.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt's G-V radioed Teterboro. Twenty minutes out.\N{\rCHT}華特的飛機在泰特波羅 20分鐘了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.60,0:40:51.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have a car waiting downstairs for me. And get me that list.\N{\rCHT}派輛車在樓下等我 把名單給我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.52,0:41:00.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Eagle One in first position. Proceeding to two.\N{\rCHT}我是鷹眼一號 在一號位 正向二號位前進{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.48,0:41:11.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bree, I asked for Dan Issa from the SEC.\N{\rCHT}布瑞 我讓你打給證交所的丹·伊薩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.48,0:41:13.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I called twice and left word both times.\N{\rCHT}我打了兩次 都留言了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.64,0:41:14.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, get me Ron.\N{\rCHT}好吧 接羅恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.48,0:41:19.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ron, I need you to go down to the SEC's offices on Vesey Street.\N{\rCHT}羅恩 你去維西街的證交所辦事處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:19.16,0:41:21.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Find Dan Issa. Do not take no for an answer. You have nine minutes.\N{\rCHT}去找丹·伊薩 不允許他們拒絕 你有9分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:21.80,0:41:22.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nine minutes?\N{\rCHT}9分鐘?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.88,0:41:25.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Vesey Street's over a mile away.  - Then you better start running now.\N{\rCHT}- 維西街離這裡一個半公里呀  - 那你就最好趕快跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:26.32,0:41:29.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, Dave, can you pull up a stock price graphic for Ibis for me, please?\N{\rCHT}戴夫 可以放一個埃比斯的股市行情圖嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.64,0:41:33.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Okay. I'll need a second.  - Okay, then put their logo up on the nine-by.\N{\rCHT}- 要等一會兒  - 好 那就先放他們的商標{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.24,0:41:34.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.16,0:41:39.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee? How many people do you think are tuned into us right now at this moment?\N{\rCHT}利? 你認為現在有多少人在看直播?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.84,0:41:42.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Millions probably? Tens of millions?\N{\rCHT}幾百萬吧? 幾千萬?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:42.76,0:41:45.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's tens of millions of investors,\N{\rCHT}那就是幾千萬個投資者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.92,0:41:49.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,all with their fingers on their E-trade accounts.\N{\rCHT}全都有電子交易帳戶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:50.00,0:41:52.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle, you bought Ibis at what, $75 a share?\N{\rCHT}科爾 埃比斯每股多少錢 75美金嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.80,0:41:56.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yeah. So?  - What if we can get it back there?\N{\rCHT}- 對 怎麼了?  - 若我們能讓它漲回來呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.84,0:41:59.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How many times I gotta tell you, it's too late for your money.\N{\rCHT}還要我說多少次 現在給我錢太晚了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:01.36,0:42:04.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're not the only shareholder that got screwed over.\N{\rCHT}你又不是唯一一個倒楣的投資者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.36,0:42:07.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You came here because you had something that you wanted to say.\N{\rCHT}你來這裡 是因為你有話要說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:07.84,0:42:09.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want people to finally listen to you, right?\N{\rCHT}你想讓大家都聽到你說吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.44,0:42:10.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.56,0:42:12.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, now they can.\N{\rCHT}現在他們就能聽到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.28,0:42:14.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Logo's ready.  - Put it up on the big screen.\N{\rCHT}- 商標準備好了  - 放上大螢幕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.04,0:42:16.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, Lee. Go to work.\N{\rCHT}好了 利 幹活吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.04,0:42:19.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Watch what we can do.\N{\rCHT}看我們能做到什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.78,0:42:19.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(埃比斯金融公司)
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.96,0:42:21.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want to talk to everybody out there.\N{\rCHT}我想跟電視機前所有人說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:21.32,0:42:23.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Every single person that's watching me right now.\N{\rCHT}你們每一個正看著我的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:23.72,0:42:25.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And here's what I want you to do.\N{\rCHT}我想讓你們這麼做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.88,0:42:27.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to go to your computer\N{\rCHT}我想你們打開電腦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.80,0:42:30.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I want you to buy Ibis stock.\N{\rCHT}買埃比斯的股票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:31.04,0:42:32.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna be upfront with you.\N{\rCHT}我跟你們實話說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.72,0:42:34.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want you to do it because you're gonna make money.\N{\rCHT}我想讓你們這麼做 不是為了讓你們賺錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:34.72,0:42:36.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to do it\N{\rCHT}我想讓你們這麼做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.04,0:42:38.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because it'll save my life.\N{\rCHT}因為這樣能救我的命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.96,0:42:41.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is ballsy.\N{\rCHT}真夠勇的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.08,0:42:43.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The old Money Monster bump.\N{\rCHT}《金錢怪獸》慣用伎倆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.40,0:42:45.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The old Money Monster bump on a massive scale.\N{\rCHT}《金錢怪獸》慣用伎倆 這次是大規模的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:47.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Where's my stock price?  - Just got it up.\N{\rCHT}- 股價圖呢?  - 剛準備好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.40,0:42:49.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's simple math. Value comes from demand.\N{\rCHT}這個計算很簡單 價值由需求決定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.80,0:42:52.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So if every single one of you buys a few shares,\N{\rCHT}若你們每人買幾個股份{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:53.00,0:42:54.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,then we can get the price of this sucker up in no time.\N{\rCHT}那麼我們就能馬上讓股價回升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.92,0:42:56.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And here's the crazy part.\N{\rCHT}瘋狂的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.76,0:42:59.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If we do it and everybody invests just a little bit of money,\N{\rCHT}若我們每人投資一點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.48,0:43:01.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the price starts to go up.\N{\rCHT}股價就會開始攀升{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.76,0:43:05.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And then the algorithms... They start to take notice, and they start to buy it.\N{\rCHT}然後演算法... 就會留意到 他們就開始買入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.04,0:43:07.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Give it to me on the big screen.\N{\rCHT}給我放到大螢幕上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:07.32,0:43:09.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If you can fool them, then the sky's the limit!\N{\rCHT}無限增長{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.36,0:43:13.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Which means that together we can turn a bad investment into a good one\N{\rCHT}也就是說 我們可以一起逆轉失敗投資{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.24,0:43:16.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,by sheer force of will.\N{\rCHT}全憑意志{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:16.44,0:43:17.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nice.\N{\rCHT}說得好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:17.76,0:43:19.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, as of right now,\N{\rCHT}所以 現在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.68,0:43:23.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am moving Ibis from a sell to a buy.\N{\rCHT}我要將埃比斯從賣出變成買進{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.72,0:43:26.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's gonna call a triple. Ready triple. Roll it.\N{\rCHT}他馬上會要"三倍" "三倍"準備 放{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.76,0:43:27.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and make it a rare...\N{\rCHT}變成罕見的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.02,0:43:29.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(買 買 買 三倍買入)
Dialogue: 0,0:43:29.24,0:43:31.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Triple Buy!\N{\rCHT}三倍買入{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.28,0:43:40.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Come on.\N{\rCHT}拜託 拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.36,0:43:51.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, you son of a bitch.\N{\rCHT}拜託 混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.92,0:43:55.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, guys.\N{\rCHT}拜託各位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:55.40,0:43:57.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're human beings, we're not computers.\N{\rCHT}我們是人 不是電腦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:58.48,0:44:00.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We have a conscience.\N{\rCHT}我們有良心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.40,0:44:02.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Refresh, refresh.\N{\rCHT}更新 更新{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.28,0:44:03.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- There it is.  - Yeah.\N{\rCHT}成功了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:03.88,0:44:05.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,$8.48.\N{\rCHT}$8.48{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.89,0:44:07.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(當前股票價格 埃比斯$8.48)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.96,0:44:08.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes! That's what I'm talking about.\N{\rCHT}好 就是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.16,0:44:10.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We take care of each other.\N{\rCHT}我們互相守望{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.48,0:44:11.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's embedded in our DNA.\N{\rCHT}這是我們與生俱來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:11.88,0:44:17.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not because an equation tells us to, but because we feel it in here.\N{\rCHT}不因為等式告訴我們如此 而是因為我們心有所感{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.80,0:44:21.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And right now, I need your help.\N{\rCHT}此刻 我需要你們的説明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.72,0:44:23.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This looks promising.\N{\rCHT}看來很有潛質{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.20,0:44:24.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We can do the right thing.\N{\rCHT}我們可以做好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.12,0:44:26.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But we have to do it together.\N{\rCHT}但我們必須同心協力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.96,0:44:28.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. Refresh, refresh.\N{\rCHT}加油 更新 更新{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.20,0:44:30.19,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(當前股票價格 埃比斯金融公司)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.29,0:44:31.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(埃比斯$8.49 利說三倍買入)
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.52,0:44:36.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, I'm talking to every one of you.\N{\rCHT}你們每一個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.64,0:44:40.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Every single person that's watching me right now.\N{\rCHT}每一個正看著我的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.72,0:44:42.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to dig as deep as you can\N{\rCHT}我希望你們挖得越深越好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.00,0:44:46.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I want you to ask yourself, what is a life worth to you?\N{\rCHT}請你們自問 一條命對於你來說值多少錢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.64,0:44:55.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's my life worth?\N{\rCHT}我的命值多少錢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.76,0:45:23.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I guess that answers that question, huh?\N{\rCHT}我想這就是問題的答案吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.28,0:45:34.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Detective, one coming in.\N{\rCHT}警探 有人來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.48,0:45:45.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ma'am. Excuse me.\N{\rCHT}女士 打擾一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.28,0:45:47.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ma'am. NYPD. You live here?\N{\rCHT}女士 我是紐約警局的 你住這裡嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.72,0:45:49.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah. What's the problem?\N{\rCHT}是呀 有事嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.32,0:45:51.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's your relationship to Kyle Budwell, ma'am?\N{\rCHT}你和科爾·巴德維爾是什麼關係?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.04,0:45:53.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why? Where is he?\N{\rCHT}怎麼了? 他在哪裡?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.28,0:45:56.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where have you been all day? If you don't mind me asking.\N{\rCHT}你一天都在哪? 若不介意我這麼問{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:56.20,0:45:58.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I work in a glass box underground for eight hours a day.\N{\rCHT}我在地鐵站的商店工作 每天8小時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:58.68,0:46:00.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So could you please just tell me what the hell is going on here,\N{\rCHT}那麼請你告訴我 到底出了什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.80,0:46:02.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because you're really starting to freak me out.\N{\rCHT}因為你真的嚇到我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.16,0:46:03.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna ask again.\N{\rCHT}我再問一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:03.52,0:46:05.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What is your relationship to Kyle Budwell, ma'am?\N{\rCHT}你和科爾·巴德維爾什麼關係?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:09.28,0:46:11.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't you take a wild guess.\N{\rCHT}你怎麼不猜一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.28,0:46:16.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Powell.\N{\rCHT}朋友?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:17.24,0:46:19.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, I'll clear a path.\N{\rCHT}好 我會清條路出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:19.80,0:46:22.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I should've taken that bet after all, you sack of shit.\N{\rCHT}我真該跟你打賭 你個混球{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.16,0:46:31.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is really impressive, Lee.\N{\rCHT}真驚奇 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.32,0:46:34.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I mean, talk about market influence.\N{\rCHT}我是說市場的影響力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:34.62,0:46:35.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(當前股票價格 埃比斯金融公司)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.96,0:46:37.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(埃比斯$8.27 利說三倍買入)
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.36,0:46:40.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you want to know why that shit didn't work, asshole?\N{\rCHT}你知道為什麼這破招不管用嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:41.92,0:46:45.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because even you don't buy your own bullshit.\N{\rCHT}因為你不買自己的破爛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.16,0:46:48.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You believe in money. You don't believe in people.\N{\rCHT}你只信錢 不信人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.84,0:46:52.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, they tracked down his girlfriend.\N{\rCHT}利 他們找到他女朋友了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.16,0:46:53.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They don't believe in you, either.\N{\rCHT}他們也不信你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.72,0:46:55.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,His pregnant girlfriend.\N{\rCHT}他女朋友懷孕了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.52,0:46:58.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You got to be fucking joking.  - No, no joke, Lee.\N{\rCHT}- 你他媽開玩笑吧  - 不是開玩笑 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.12,0:47:01.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Quant.\N{\rCHT}分析師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.24,0:47:03.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Quantitative analytics.\N{\rCHT}定量分析師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.56,0:47:05.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, I have no idea what you're saying right now.\N{\rCHT}我現在聽不懂你說什麼 你們有人說英語嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.76,0:47:07.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Does anybody there speak English?\N{\rCHT}這裡有人會說英語嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.32,0:47:12.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fuck.\N{\rCHT}操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.40,0:47:13.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I need the other number for the guy in Moscow.\N{\rCHT}我要那個莫斯科人的另一個號碼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.00,0:47:17.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, but he gave me another name. This one's based out of Seoul.\N{\rCHT}好 但他給了我另一個人 是首爾的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.41,0:47:20.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(登入用戶名萊斯特)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.00,0:47:21.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(登入失敗 用戶名無效)
Dialogue: 0,0:47:22.24,0:47:24.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God damn it. Goodloe.\N{\rCHT}該死的 古德洛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.36,0:47:33.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Shit.  - I've got it.\N{\rCHT}我來吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.16,0:47:36.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go get me a phone number. I'm gonna find a translator.\N{\rCHT}給我電話號碼 我會去找個翻譯來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:43.92,0:47:46.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Amy! Amy! Amy!\N{\rCHT}艾米 艾米 艾米{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.56,0:47:49.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bring your security pass and come with me.\N{\rCHT}帶上你的職員證跟我來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.76,0:47:55.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hurts, doesn't it?\N{\rCHT}心疼吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got your fancy education.\N{\rCHT}得到教訓了吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:59.08,0:48:01.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Got your millions in the bank.\N{\rCHT}銀行裡幾百萬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:01.92,0:48:03.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Think you got it all made.\N{\rCHT}以為都賺到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.24,0:48:08.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're not such a hot shit right now, huh?\N{\rCHT}你現在沒那麼紅吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.68,0:48:15.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to sit here and take stock of our lives, Kyle?\N{\rCHT}你想坐在這 賭上我們的性命嗎 科爾?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.00,0:48:18.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How about we compare scores?\N{\rCHT}我們來比比分數如何{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.52,0:48:19.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How about we do that?\N{\rCHT}怎麼樣?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.88,0:48:22.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Touchscreen. Shit, the touchscreen.\N{\rCHT}觸屏 該死 他要用觸屏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:24.76,0:48:28.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. We got Kyle and we got Lee.\N{\rCHT}好 這邊是科爾 這邊是利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:28.32,0:48:29.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(分數板 科爾 利)
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.80,0:48:32.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's start with the obvious. Money.\N{\rCHT}從最顯而易見的開始 錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:32.16,0:48:34.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got some. You don't, I gather.\N{\rCHT}我有 但我想你沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:35.28,0:48:36.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, that's a point for me.\N{\rCHT}那我就得一分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:37.44,0:48:38.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where you going with this, Lee?\N{\rCHT}你要幹什麼 利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:38.60,0:48:40.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But then there's family.\N{\rCHT}但是還有家人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.72,0:48:43.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm divorced three times. What about you? You got a wife?\N{\rCHT}我離過三次婚 你呢? 有妻子嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.84,0:48:45.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Girlfriend, then?\N{\rCHT}有女朋友嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:46.04,0:48:47.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sacajawea, Lee.\N{\rCHT}薩卡加維亞 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:47.32,0:48:51.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got a girlfriend? That's nice. The magic of young love.\N{\rCHT}你有女朋友? 很好 年輕人神奇的愛情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:51.24,0:48:52.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I think we can both agree that's a point for you,\N{\rCHT}我想我們倆都同意你得一分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.04,0:48:56.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,since the first number on my speed-dial is an escort service.\N{\rCHT}因為我設置的第一個快速撥號 是個三陪小姐{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.64,0:48:59.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You don't know anything about me.  - I don't need to know about you!\N{\rCHT}- 你不瞭解我  - 不需要瞭解你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:59.28,0:49:02.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I know about me. Seven years, three years, 14 months.\N{\rCHT}我瞭解我自己 七年 三年 14個月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:02.68,0:49:04.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The marriages, they get shorter and they get shorter,\N{\rCHT}婚姻越來越短{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.64,0:49:06.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but settlements, they get larger and larger.\N{\rCHT}但贍養費越來越多{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.92,0:49:07.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee?\N{\rCHT}利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.04,0:49:09.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at me, Lee.\N{\rCHT}利 看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.68,0:49:12.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sacajawea.\N{\rCHT}薩卡加維亞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:13.12,0:49:15.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, Kyle, you see her?\N{\rCHT}科爾 你看到她了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:15.88,0:49:19.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's Patty, my director, and she wants me to shut up.\N{\rCHT}那是帕蒂 我的導演 她想讓我閉嘴{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.88,0:49:22.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, now, she's sick of me, too.\N{\rCHT}她現在也很討厭我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.80,0:49:27.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's why she took a job across the street and didn't tell me.\N{\rCHT}因此她瞞著我 跳槽到街對面去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.80,0:49:32.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,People talk.\N{\rCHT}人言可畏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.92,0:49:35.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They all leave sooner or later, Kyle. That's just how it works.\N{\rCHT}他們遲早都會離開 科爾 就是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.84,0:49:38.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So trust me, that's gonna be a point for you.\N{\rCHT}所以相信我 這一分是你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.68,0:49:41.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about kids?\N{\rCHT}孩子呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:42.92,0:49:44.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got a kid?\N{\rCHT}你有孩子嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.20,0:49:48.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One on the way, maybe?\N{\rCHT}也許正懷著一個?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.08,0:49:51.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah? She's expecting. It's a blessing.\N{\rCHT}是嗎? 她懷孕了 真幸福{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:51.88,0:49:54.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have one myself.\N{\rCHT}我自己也有個孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.12,0:49:58.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She must be six or seven. I have no idea.\N{\rCHT}她應該六七歲了 我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:58.44,0:49:59.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I send a check.\N{\rCHT}我寄張支票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.12,0:50:02.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mazel tov on the bundle of joy.\N{\rCHT}祝賀喜得貴子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.96,0:50:05.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I think we can both agree that's another fucking point for you.\N{\rCHT}我想你我都同意你他媽又得一分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.76,0:50:07.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, now, look at this.\N{\rCHT}你看看吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.32,0:50:10.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle. Oh, my God. We just got started and you're already ahead.\N{\rCHT}科爾 天呀 我們才剛開始 你就已經領先了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.56,0:50:12.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just... Just stay wide, Jim.\N{\rCHT}保持遠景鏡頭 吉姆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.48,0:50:14.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So let me ask you something, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}我問你 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.40,0:50:18.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about your life is so much shittier than the rest of ours\N{\rCHT}既然你的生活比別人的都糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.48,0:50:20.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that you get to throw in the towel early?\N{\rCHT}那麼提早結束如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.48,0:50:22.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want to know.\N{\rCHT}我想知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:23.32,0:50:25.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got a decent job. You got two hands and two feet.\N{\rCHT}你有個體面工作 手腳齊全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:25.64,0:50:27.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got a goddamn kid on the way!\N{\rCHT}馬上就要有孩子了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.32,0:50:32.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So before you blow me to kingdom come, I want you to answer one question.\N{\rCHT}在你把我炸開花之前 我想你回答一個問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.64,0:50:35.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What makes you such a giant fucking failure compared to everybody else?\N{\rCHT}為什麼跟別人比起來 你他媽如此狼狽?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:35.76,0:50:37.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You really gonna stand there in your $1,000 suit\N{\rCHT}你穿著一千美金的西裝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.52,0:50:39.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and compare scores with me?\N{\rCHT}還跟我比分數?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.16,0:50:44.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My honest job pays me $14 an hour, you cocksucker.\N{\rCHT}我老老實實工作 一個小時才賺14美金 你個混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.44,0:50:46.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So let's start there.\N{\rCHT}從這個開始吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:47.08,0:50:50.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know how far $14 an hour gets you here in New York?\N{\rCHT}你知道一小時14美金 在紐約能幹什麼嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.16,0:50:54.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know how much of that is left after I pay my rent and all my fucking bills?\N{\rCHT}你知道付了房租和所有帳單之後還剩多少嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.12,0:50:58.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I keep paddling as hard as I can just to stay above water.\N{\rCHT}我全力以赴維持生計{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.00,0:51:00.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It takes everything I got!\N{\rCHT}我的一切都沒了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.36,0:51:01.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And that's before the kid gets here.\N{\rCHT}這發生在我孩子降生之前{\r}
