Dialogue: 0,0:56:40.64,0:56:43.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And this algo was designed to move in and out\N{\rCHT}這個演算法是用來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:43.64,0:56:45.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of hundreds of positions in fractions of seconds.\N{\rCHT}在短短幾秒鐘 買賣成百上千個倉位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.08,0:56:47.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.16,0:56:51.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What it wasn't designed to do is consume large amounts of capital,\N{\rCHT}而不是用來消化大量資金的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.00,0:56:54.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,accumulate leveraged positions or...\N{\rCHT}或積累杠杆倉 或...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.20,0:56:58.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Or hold a portfolio for any extended period of time.\N{\rCHT}長時間維持投資組合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.16,0:57:00.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait. What does that mean?\N{\rCHT}等等 什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:00.28,0:57:02.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It means\N{\rCHT}意思是說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:02.16,0:57:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,there is no way that this algorithm\N{\rCHT}這個演算法不可能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.60,0:57:08.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,could lose $800 million in one afternoon.\N{\rCHT}一個下午就賠八個億{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.96,0:57:12.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It is literally a mathematical impossibility.\N{\rCHT}數學上來講 是絕對不可能的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:13.36,0:57:16.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So whatever went wrong, whatever investment went haywire,\N{\rCHT}所以無論什麼問題 無論投資如何失敗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.52,0:57:18.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's not the computer's fault.\N{\rCHT}都不是電腦的錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.92,0:57:23.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's human fingerprints all over this.\N{\rCHT}全部都是人的錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.96,0:57:25.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Whose fingerprints?\N{\rCHT}哪個人的錯?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:25.96,0:57:30.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Like I said, I don't want to get involved in this.\N{\rCHT}我說了 我不想被捲進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:30.40,0:57:32.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is there anything you can give me?\N{\rCHT}你能給我些信息嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.20,0:57:33.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do the math.\N{\rCHT}你自己算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.44,0:57:37.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can't find your boss, and he can't find $800 million.\N{\rCHT}你找不到你老闆 你老闆也找不回來八億美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:37.96,0:57:40.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where did you say he was coming from?\N{\rCHT}你說他剛去完哪裡回來?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.12,0:57:42.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What a mess, huh?\N{\rCHT}一團亂是嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:43.36,0:57:44.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I take it you've heard by now?\N{\rCHT}我想你已經聽說了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.00,0:57:46.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.64,0:57:49.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goodloe started calling me the second I turned my phone back on.\N{\rCHT}我剛開手機 古德洛就不停打{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:49.92,0:57:52.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He and I had a disagreement over strategy.\N{\rCHT}他和我就辦事策略發生了衝突{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.96,0:57:54.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So I heard.\N{\rCHT}我聽說了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.36,0:57:57.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You did good.\N{\rCHT}你做得很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.04,0:58:01.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm proud of you... Whatever Goodloe says.\N{\rCHT}我為你自豪... 別管古德洛說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:04.96,0:58:06.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Here, I got you some chocolate.\N{\rCHT}我給你買了些巧克力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.72,0:58:09.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,From Switzerland.\N{\rCHT}瑞士的吻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.04,0:58:16.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, I'll take those and put them in the back for you.\N{\rCHT}我幫你把行李放到車後面去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.92,0:58:33.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(護照 入境 南非)
Dialogue: 0,0:58:34.08,0:58:35.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's cold.\N{\rCHT}真冷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.00,0:58:38.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Amy, can you sit up front, please?\N{\rCHT}艾米 請你坐前面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:38.76,0:58:40.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And don't say a fucking word.\N{\rCHT}什麼都別說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.92,0:58:53.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's right. She's fucking right. She's fucking right.\N{\rCHT}她說的對 她說的對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.24,0:58:55.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's fucking right!\N{\rCHT}她說的對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.08,0:59:00.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God damn it! Jesus.\N{\rCHT}該死 天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.96,0:59:02.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God, why do you always do this?\N{\rCHT}天 你總這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.28,0:59:03.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This isn't good, Lee.\N{\rCHT}這不好 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:03.96,0:59:06.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're so stupid, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}你太蠢了 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.20,0:59:08.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're so stupid, you stupid pussy.\N{\rCHT}你真蠢 你個蠢蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.32,0:59:12.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's fucking right.\N{\rCHT}她說的對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.60,0:59:13.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now what?\N{\rCHT}現在怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:13.80,0:59:16.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the fuck am I fucking doing?\N{\rCHT}我他媽該怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.48,0:59:17.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shit!\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.84,0:59:20.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not...\N{\rCHT}別...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:21.48,0:59:22.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll do it.\N{\rCHT}我會做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.80,0:59:25.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got to fucking do it.\N{\rCHT}你要做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.32,0:59:28.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got to fucking do it. You stupid piece of fucking shit.\N{\rCHT}我要做 你他媽的混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.36,0:59:37.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the fuck am I fucking doing? I've got to do this.\N{\rCHT}我該怎麼辦? 我馬上就做{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.24,0:59:38.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle.\N{\rCHT}科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:53.28,0:59:55.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What am I gonna do? Shoot you?\N{\rCHT}我該怎麼辦? 斃了你?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:59:56.44,0:59:58.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't want to shoot you, Kyle. I don't want you to die.\N{\rCHT}我不想斃了你 科爾 我不想你死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:00.08,1:00:01.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What chance do I have now?\N{\rCHT}我還能怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:02.40,1:00:05.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's still a way out of this. I know there's still a way out.\N{\rCHT}還有解決辦法 我知道還有辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.56,1:00:07.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell me one reason why I shouldn't put this gun in my mouth\N{\rCHT}給我一個不開槍打死自己{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:07.76,1:00:09.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and pull the fucking trigger.\N{\rCHT}還有不引爆炸彈的理由{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.48,1:00:11.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle, look at me.\N{\rCHT}科爾 看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:12.40,1:00:13.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey.\N{\rCHT}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.68,1:00:15.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You made a mistake.\N{\rCHT}你犯了個錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.88,1:00:18.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That doesn't mean your life is over.\N{\rCHT}並不意味著你該結束生命{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:18.88,1:00:20.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What you need is a plan.\N{\rCHT}你需要的是計畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:20.52,1:00:22.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No way any plan's gonna help me through this.\N{\rCHT}沒什麼計畫能幫我度過這個難關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:22.36,1:00:24.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's 'cause you're not thinking straight.\N{\rCHT}因為你沒好好想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.04,1:00:27.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm willing to help you if you'll let me.\N{\rCHT}我願意幫你 只要你讓我幫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:28.88,1:00:30.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Step one.\N{\rCHT}第一步{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:30.68,1:00:34.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This gun and this vest is not helping anything.\N{\rCHT}這把槍和這個背心一點用都沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:34.24,1:00:37.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I know what you're trying to do.  - Signals get crossed. Things get chaotic.\N{\rCHT}- 我知道你想幹什麼  - 目的達到了 事情變一團糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:37.40,1:00:39.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Innocent people get hurt. It happens all the time.\N{\rCHT}無辜的人受傷 總是這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.36,1:00:43.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If I let any of these guys go then I'm dead.\N{\rCHT}我要是讓這些人走了 我就死定了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:43.68,1:00:45.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.40,1:00:47.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus.\N{\rCHT}天呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.52,1:00:50.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right.\N{\rCHT}好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.80,1:00:52.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll find another way.\N{\rCHT}再想個別的辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:53.40,1:00:57.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You got to give me some space. I need to rethink this.\N{\rCHT}你容我再好好想想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.12,1:01:02.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is Fox 2 in position? Make your move.\N{\rCHT}二號狐狸就位了嗎? 行動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:04.52,1:01:06.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A plan, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}計畫 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:06.40,1:01:08.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's all we need.\N{\rCHT}我們只需要計畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:25.04,1:01:27.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We just got unobstructed access, north side studio.\N{\rCHT}我們剛到無遮擋位置 在攝影棚北邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:27.60,1:01:30.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Repeat. Unobstructed access on the north.\N{\rCHT}重複 攝影棚北邊無遮擋位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.16,1:01:32.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Go with him. Extraction only, though.  - Sir.\N{\rCHT}- 跟他去 只進行疏散  - 好的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.80,1:01:34.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you understand? Extraction only right now.\N{\rCHT}你們明白嗎? 現在只進行疏散{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.90,1:01:37.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(曼博情況如何?)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.61,1:01:41.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(曼博凍結)
Dialogue: 0,1:01:43.44,1:01:46.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, I agree with you. We need to get ahead of this one.\N{\rCHT}聽著 我同意你說的 我們需要提前著手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:47.36,1:01:49.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And we're all about transparency, after all.\N{\rCHT}我是說 我們終究要公開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:50.04,1:01:53.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm the CEO, so I'm the one who needs to make the statement.\N{\rCHT}我是首席行政長官 所以應該我來發表聲明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.24,1:01:55.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We just need to make sure it's on our terms, not on theirs.\N{\rCHT}我們只需保證對我們有利 而非有利於他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.36,1:01:56.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're all set up at Federal Hall.\N{\rCHT}我們在聯邦紀念堂做準備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.08,1:02:00.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We have the run of the place, we have security onsite,\N{\rCHT}我們有權使用那個地方 那裡有我們的保安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.16,1:02:01.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and no one knows you'll be going there.\N{\rCHT}沒人知道你會去那裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:04.92,1:02:06.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're going in.\N{\rCHT}我們進來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:15.84,1:02:17.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We got company.\N{\rCHT}我們有支援了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.16,1:02:18.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Three, show me.\N{\rCHT}三號機 讓我看看{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.16,1:02:28.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, as long as it's controlled.\N{\rCHT}好 只要能控制{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.44,1:02:32.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Give an exclusive to somebody you trust.\N{\rCHT}給你信任的人一個獨家報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.48,1:02:34.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I know just the person to call.\N{\rCHT}我知道該叫誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.76,1:02:36.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's my girl.\N{\rCHT}真是乖孩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.84,1:02:38.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, Lenny?\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 可以嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.92,1:02:43.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I want you to push in. Block as much of his view as you can.\N{\rCHT}你推進去一些 儘量擋住他的視線{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:46.36,1:02:47.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee?\N{\rCHT}利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.76,1:02:49.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not make a move.\N{\rCHT}別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.36,1:02:51.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If he turns around,\N{\rCHT}他若轉身看到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.00,1:02:53.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we are all gonna die.\N{\rCHT}我們就都死定了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.24,1:03:18.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, Lenny.\N{\rCHT}好吧 蘭尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:18.56,1:03:20.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're the last manned camera.\N{\rCHT}你是最後一個攝影師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.04,1:03:27.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Balls.\N{\rCHT}做個漢子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.32,1:03:30.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty Fenn.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂·芬恩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.88,1:03:32.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, Diane Lester.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 黛安·萊斯特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.52,1:03:35.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You better have something for me, Diane, and I mean, right the fuck now.\N{\rCHT}你最好說些有用的 黛安 趕快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.88,1:03:37.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's good to hear your voice, too.\N{\rCHT}我也很高興聽到你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.56,1:03:39.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm calling you to let you know the information I gave you\N{\rCHT}我想說之前給你的資訊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.08,1:03:41.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,might have been incorrect.\N{\rCHT}可能不太正確{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.56,1:03:43.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What the hell does that mean? "Incorrect"?\N{\rCHT}什麼意思? 不正確?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.08,1:03:46.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt is going to make a statement after all.\N{\rCHT}華特終究還是要發表聲明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.40,1:03:48.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're in the car en route to Federal Hall right now.\N{\rCHT}我們正坐車去聯邦紀念堂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.60,1:03:50.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We'll be about 20 minutes away.\N{\rCHT}大約20分鐘後到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.12,1:03:52.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Twenty minutes? We need help right now!\N{\rCHT}20分鐘? 我們現在就需要幫助{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.08,1:03:55.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm trying to help you, if you'll just listen.\N{\rCHT}我會盡力幫助你 只要你聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:55.24,1:03:57.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to send you a text explaining what I need from you.\N{\rCHT}我會給你發個資訊 告訴你我需要你怎麼配合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.84,1:03:59.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So just keep a lid on it.\N{\rCHT}要保密{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.12,1:04:02.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because I'm giving you this exclusively. Don't screw it up.\N{\rCHT}因為這是只給你一個人的 別洩密{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.24,1:04:06.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Reporters.\N{\rCHT}記者們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.72,1:04:09.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello? Diane?\N{\rCHT}喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.24,1:04:11.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, everybody. We're gonna begin evacuation one at a time.\N{\rCHT}好吧各位 我們一次疏散一個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.76,1:04:13.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You first. Follow me to the crawlspace.\N{\rCHT}你先出來 跟我到走廊去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.04,1:04:19.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're ready and in position. Give me the green light, we go.\N{\rCHT}準備就緒 給我們指示我們就行動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.72,1:04:22.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If we take out the receiver on Gates' chest, what's his chance of survival?\N{\rCHT}我們若射擊蓋茲胸前的接收器 他的生還幾率多大?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.80,1:04:23.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,80% that he makes it.\N{\rCHT}80%的可能性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.08,1:04:26.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. What's the chance the bullet's on target?\N{\rCHT}好吧 命中目標的幾率呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.56,1:04:30.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- If it's a clean shot, 100%.  - 100%. Come on, let's be realistic here.\N{\rCHT}- 無障礙射擊 100%命中  - 100% 得了吧 現實些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.24,1:04:32.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I am being. Listen, 80% sounds about right to us, to an officer.\N{\rCHT}我很現實 80%還說得過去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.92,1:04:33.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,80%.\N{\rCHT}80%{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.08,1:04:38.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So we got an 80% chance of an 80% chance. Yeah, that's some shit math.\N{\rCHT}那我們就是80%機會中的80% 是這麼算吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:38.64,1:04:42.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Benson, let me know when the control room is ready to evacuate.\N{\rCHT}本森 控制室清空後告訴我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:47.13,1:04:49.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(黛安·萊斯特 華特沒去日內瓦 他去了南非)
Dialogue: 0,1:04:49.52,1:04:50.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now we're talking.\N{\rCHT}終於給了點有用的資訊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.96,1:04:52.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, guys,\N{\rCHT}好了 各位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.32,1:04:55.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,how do we find out what Walt Camby's jet was doing in South Africa?\N{\rCHT}我們如何能查到 華特·坎比的飛機去南非幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:55.96,1:04:58.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- We could try the FAA.  - No, they won't help us.\N{\rCHT}- 我們可以試試聯邦航空管理局  - 不行 他們才不會幫我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.20,1:05:03.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about the hacker guy from the Citi security breach segment?\N{\rCHT}花旗銀行保安部那個駭客呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:03.60,1:05:06.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- The guy with the Yoda voice.  - Yes! Yes! Find him. Quickly.\N{\rCHT}- 嗓音像尤達的那個人  - 對 就是他 快點兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:08.96,1:05:11.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Watch your head. Step here.\N{\rCHT}小心你的頭 踩這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.88,1:05:17.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bree, where the hell is Ron Sprecher? And has he gotten to the SEC yet?\N{\rCHT}布瑞 羅恩·斯普雷徹在哪? 他到證交所了嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.68,1:05:20.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I will check, but I need to tell you something first.\N{\rCHT}我來看看 但我要先告訴你件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:20.68,1:05:22.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, hold on. Just a second.\N{\rCHT}好 等一下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:22.16,1:05:23.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, Walt Camby has landed.\N{\rCHT}利 華特·坎比降落了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.96,1:05:25.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's on his way to Federal Hall.\N{\rCHT}他在去聯邦紀念堂路上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.40,1:05:26.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He'll be there in less than 20 minutes.\N{\rCHT}20分鐘內到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:26.84,1:05:30.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And get this. He wasn't in Geneva yesterday. He was in South Africa.\N{\rCHT}還有 他昨天沒去日內瓦 他去了南非{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.08,1:05:33.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So he lied to you. He lied to us.\N{\rCHT}他騙了你 騙了我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.16,1:05:37.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's been lying this whole time. That means you've been lying, too, Lee.\N{\rCHT}他一直在撒謊 也就是說你也一直在撒謊 利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.00,1:05:41.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,To everybody that's been watching. To Kyle.\N{\rCHT}騙了所有觀眾 包括科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.28,1:05:43.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Oh, my God.\N{\rCHT}操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.88,1:05:45.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where'd everybody go?\N{\rCHT}大家都哪去了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:48.36,1:05:49.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where'd they go?\N{\rCHT}他們都去哪了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.12,1:05:54.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,God damn it!\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:54.84,1:05:56.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I knew this would happen.\N{\rCHT}我就知道會這樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.52,1:05:58.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Let's go. Who's next?  - Charlie, in the sound booth.\N{\rCHT}- 走吧 下一個是誰?  - 查理 在音效室裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:58.72,1:05:59.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How stupid am I?\N{\rCHT}我有多傻?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.80,1:06:01.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. Quick as you can.\N{\rCHT}好 儘快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.20,1:06:02.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get those hackers working.\N{\rCHT}讓那些駭客快些{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.92,1:06:04.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's all your fault, Lee. You so stupid.\N{\rCHT}都是你的錯 利 你很愚蠢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:04.79,1:06:05.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(資訊已發送)
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.88,1:06:09.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(我們被綁架了 需要你的説明)
Dialogue: 0,1:06:09.54,1:06:11.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(請立即回電 十萬火急)
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.12,1:06:31.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Dave.\N{\rCHT}我是戴夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:31.80,1:06:33.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got your email, Dave.\N{\rCHT}我收到你的電郵了 戴夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.44,1:06:38.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Help you, we will.\N{\rCHT}我們會幫你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:42.36,1:06:44.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Eagle One. Target is in position.\N{\rCHT}我是鷹眼一號 目標就位{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.80,1:06:46.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bunch of crooks.\N{\rCHT}一群混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:48.08,1:06:50.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Camby's never coming here. We have to figure out a way, Kyle.\N{\rCHT}坎比永遠不會來了 我們得想個法子 科爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:50.68,1:06:52.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty, I really need to tell you something.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 我真的有話要說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:52.92,1:06:54.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, hold on, just a second, Bree.\N{\rCHT}好 等一下 布瑞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:54.60,1:06:56.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No! Damn it! You need to hear this.\N{\rCHT}不行 該死的 你必須聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.12,1:06:59.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. What is it?\N{\rCHT}好 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:59.44,1:07:01.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't stop. Don't panic. Stay low.\N{\rCHT}別停下 別慌 別站起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.68,1:07:04.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm so fucked!\N{\rCHT}我死定了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.20,1:07:07.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Eagle, Do you have a clean shot?  - I'm yellow. Yellow.\N{\rCHT}- 鷹眼 射程內有障礙嗎?  - 部分障礙 部分{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.40,1:07:08.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you sure?  - Positive.\N{\rCHT}- 真的?  - 真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:08.92,1:07:11.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're going to shoot Lee. I heard every word. I was five-feet away.\N{\rCHT}他們要對利射擊 我距離他們只有一米半 都聽到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.28,1:07:13.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go. This isn't voluntary.\N{\rCHT}不管你願不願意{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.20,1:07:14.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Grab whatever you can grab.  - Jim. Take Jim.\N{\rCHT}- 收拾東西  - 讓吉姆走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:15.60,1:07:16.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Let's go.  - Be careful.\N{\rCHT}- 走吧  - 小心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.96,1:07:21.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I can't catch a fucking break.\N{\rCHT}我倒楣透了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:21.48,1:07:23.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm never getting out of here. Fuck!\N{\rCHT}我永遠也出不去了 操{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:23.28,1:07:24.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee.\N{\rCHT}利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.36,1:07:26.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're making us leave.\N{\rCHT}他們在疏散我們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.56,1:07:28.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Don't stop. It's gonna be fine.  - I'm good. Get Patty.\N{\rCHT}- 不要停下 別怕  - 我沒事 讓帕蒂走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.32,1:07:30.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at me.\N{\rCHT}看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:30.76,1:07:32.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't look up. Look at me.\N{\rCHT}別看上面 看我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.48,1:07:36.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There is a sniper on the catwalk at your one o'clock.\N{\rCHT}走廊上有個狙擊手 就在你現在1點鐘位置{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:37.24,1:07:38.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where'd they fucking go?\N{\rCHT}他們幹什麼呢?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.16,1:07:41.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's about to lose it, Benson.\N{\rCHT}他要鬆開關了 本森{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:41.52,1:07:44.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hold on. I got one lagging.  - Benson, hurry the hell up!\N{\rCHT}- 等等 有個人不配合  - 快點兒走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.12,1:07:46.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There is a receiver on your vest.\N{\rCHT}你背心上有個接收器{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:47.16,1:07:48.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Two seconds, I pull out my cuffs.  - Don't look down.\N{\rCHT}- 再等兩秒鐘我就用手銬了  - 別看下麵{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.56,1:07:52.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If he shoots it out, it disables the trigger.\N{\rCHT}如果他射中了 就能讓引爆開關失靈{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.56,1:07:53.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get out of there, right now!\N{\rCHT}快走 快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:53.88,1:07:54.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on!\N{\rCHT}走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.96,1:07:56.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You got a shot?  - Are you green or red?\N{\rCHT}- 射程有障礙嗎?  - 有沒有?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.96,1:07:58.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Green.  - Take the shot!\N{\rCHT}- 沒有  - 開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.80,1:08:03.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What are you doing? What are you doing?  - Fuck!\N{\rCHT}你幹什麼? 你幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:03.64,1:08:05.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The button!\N{\rCHT}開關 開關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.80,1:08:07.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Are you all right?  - What the fuck?\N{\rCHT}- 你沒事吧?  - 什麼鬼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.24,1:08:09.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're shooting at me, not you! God damn it!\N{\rCHT}他們是對我開槍 不是你 混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.88,1:08:15.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just keep your finger on the button.\N{\rCHT}按住開關別動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.20,1:08:16.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, can you hear me?\N{\rCHT}利 聽得到嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.80,1:08:20.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What is this? You been talking to the cops this whole time?\N{\rCHT}這是什麼? 你一直在跟員警聯絡?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.44,1:08:21.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's Patty.\N{\rCHT}是帕蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.60,1:08:23.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen to me!\N{\rCHT}聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.36,1:08:26.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She found Walt Camby.\N{\rCHT}她找到華特·坎比了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.36,1:08:30.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna take you to him. But you got to trust me.\N{\rCHT}我會帶你去見他 但你要相信我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.60,1:08:32.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I got a plan.\N{\rCHT}我有主意了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.48,1:08:34.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, you got to block my vest.\N{\rCHT}聽著你要擋住我的背心{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.52,1:08:39.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go.\N{\rCHT}走{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.96,1:08:43.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Hey, wait. What are we doing?  - We're getting out of here.\N{\rCHT}- 等等 幹什麼?  - 離開這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.52,1:08:45.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Give me the mike.\N{\rCHT}給我話筒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.40,1:08:49.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you setting me up?\N{\rCHT}你這是陷害我嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.40,1:08:52.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want some answers? We're gonna get some answers.\N{\rCHT}你想要個說法嗎? 我們就去討個說法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:52.48,1:08:53.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny, you coming?\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 你來嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.88,1:08:55.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're coming out!\N{\rCHT}我們出來啦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:59.55,1:09:01.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(錄影中)
Dialogue: 0,1:09:08.08,1:09:09.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny.\N{\rCHT}蘭尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.52,1:09:10.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You mind?\N{\rCHT}你不介意吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:12.52,1:09:13.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Balls.\N{\rCHT}漢子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.72,1:09:20.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Holy shit.\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.12,1:09:23.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- What's the matter with you?  - I don't like elevators.\N{\rCHT}- 你怎麼了?  - 我不喜歡搭電梯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:24.72,1:09:26.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Lenny.\N{\rCHT}拜託 蘭尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.44,1:09:28.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny, where are you?\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 你在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.44,1:09:31.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What did I ever do to deserve such a loyal goddamn crew, Lenny?\N{\rCHT}我做了什麼好事 配得上這麼衷心的員工?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:31.88,1:09:33.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Not much.  - That's right.\N{\rCHT}- 沒幹什麼好事  - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.52,1:09:36.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I need a satellite van and an audio package downstairs in two minutes.\N{\rCHT}兩分鐘後 給我準備一輛衛星車和音效設備{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.64,1:09:39.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lenny, where are you?\N{\rCHT}蘭尼 你在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.24,1:09:41.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jim, where's my feed with Lenny? I need it right now.\N{\rCHT}吉姆 蘭尼拍的鏡頭呢? 馬上給我放出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.04,1:09:43.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on, Lenny.\N{\rCHT}拜託 蘭尼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.60,1:09:46.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty tells us to stay, we stay.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂讓我們留下 我們就留下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.24,1:09:47.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, Lenny's up! He's live.\N{\rCHT}好了 蘭尼的攝像機出現了 他在直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.12,1:09:50.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, Patty. It's always Patty.\N{\rCHT}對 帕蒂 總是帕蒂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:51.36,1:09:54.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My first day on the job she told me I had a penis where my brain should be.\N{\rCHT}我上班第一天她就告訴我 我沒腦子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:55.52,1:09:57.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She's right. She's always right.\N{\rCHT}她說的對 從來都是對的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.56,1:09:59.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She stayed here longer than she should have.\N{\rCHT}她不需要留在這裡這麼久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.08,1:10:01.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I know that.\N{\rCHT}我知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.44,1:10:05.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The truth is I don't know what I'd do without her at this point.\N{\rCHT}事實是我不知道 要是沒有她我可怎麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.68,1:10:09.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But if she was standing right here, right now, I couldn't admit that.\N{\rCHT}但若她此刻站在這裡 我就說不出這些話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:10.96,1:10:15.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But luckily it's just you in front of me, Lenny. You and your...\N{\rCHT}但有幸只有你在我跟前 蘭尼 你和你的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:15.48,1:10:17.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your warm eyes and your gentle soul.\N{\rCHT}你的溫柔眼神和溫順人格{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.76,1:10:19.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right, get the fuck out of here.\N{\rCHT}好啦 快他媽離開這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.64,1:10:22.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I got a signal.  - Okay, are we live?\N{\rCHT}- 我收到信號了  - 好吧 我們是直播嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.60,1:10:25.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Time to find Diane Lester. Let's go.\N{\rCHT}該去找黛安·萊斯特了 走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.32,1:10:27.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- If you're still with us, here we go.  - Come on.\N{\rCHT}你若還在看 我們出發了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:11.36,1:11:12.93,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- We're going that way, Lenny. That way.  - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 走那邊 蘭尼 那邊  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:17.40,1:11:18.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Captain.  - No.\N{\rCHT}- 警監  - 不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.60,1:11:24.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're on the move. Clear a path.\N{\rCHT}移動中 清路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.20,1:11:30.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- That van comes with us!  - Clear the sat van.\N{\rCHT}- 那輛車跟我們走  - 清空那輛車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:30.28,1:11:31.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are these people doing here?\N{\rCHT}這麼多人在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:31.76,1:11:33.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now they've left the building.\N{\rCHT}他們已經離開大樓了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:33.36,1:11:34.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They are taking to the streets.\N{\rCHT}他們走街上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.88,1:11:39.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kyle Budwell and host Lee Gates seem to be working together at this point.\N{\rCHT}財經有線電視人質危機 《金錢怪獸》行動起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:35.66,1:11:40.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(科爾·巴德維爾和利·蓋茲 現在似乎在合作)
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.20,1:11:44.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello?\N{\rCHT}喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.32,1:11:46.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're on our way to you now, but we need something more.\N{\rCHT}我們正在去你們那邊 但我們需要更多消息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:46.52,1:11:48.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We've figured out where, we need to find out why.\N{\rCHT}我們知道他去了哪兒 但我們還需要知道為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:48.96,1:11:50.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's been lying about everything.\N{\rCHT}他一直都在撒謊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:50.52,1:11:53.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Keep him away from the news until we figure out the connection.\N{\rCHT}別讓他看新聞 等我們查出原因再說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.32,1:11:54.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I understand.\N{\rCHT}明白了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:01.00,1:12:03.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Here. You should put your suit on.\N{\rCHT}給你 換上西裝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:03.44,1:12:05.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll come back up for you once they're all set up.\N{\rCHT}他們準備好之後我會回來接你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:05.60,1:12:06.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:09.52,1:12:11.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jim, throw the feed into my sat van.\N{\rCHT}吉姆 把畫面放到我的衛星轉播車上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:11.96,1:12:15.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You stay with Lenny on foot. We're gonna go nat sound from his camera.\N{\rCHT}你跟蘭尼步行過去 我們會從他的攝像機收聲音{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:15.12,1:12:17.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where the hell is Ron Sprecher?\N{\rCHT}羅恩·斯普雷徹在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.76,1:12:20.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Patty! I just left the SEC. I've been trying to call you.\N{\rCHT}帕蒂 我剛離開證交所 我一直在試著打你電話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:20.44,1:12:21.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, Ron, listen.\N{\rCHT}羅恩 聽著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.56,1:12:22.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Yeah, they got nothing over here.  - What?\N{\rCHT}- 他們什麼都沒有  - 什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:22.88,1:12:25.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ibis's algorithm trades in dark pools,\N{\rCHT}埃比斯的演算法是黑市交易{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.44,1:12:27.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,so all their transactions are concealed.\N{\rCHT}所以他們所有資金往來 都是秘密進行的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:27.52,1:12:30.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The one thing I was able to find out was, on the day of the crash,\N{\rCHT}我只查到一件事 就是出事那天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:31.04,1:12:32.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ibis's transaction volume\N{\rCHT}埃比斯的交易量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.84,1:12:34.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,dropped by nearly 90%.\N{\rCHT}驟降90%{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.88,1:12:36.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What does that mean?\N{\rCHT}這是什麼意思?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.76,1:12:38.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know.\N{\rCHT}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:38.60,1:12:39.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How far away are you?\N{\rCHT}你離我們多遠?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:39.80,1:12:41.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm on... Where am I? I'm on Vesey Street.\N{\rCHT}我... 我在哪? 我在維西街{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.68,1:12:44.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bring me what you have, Ron. I'll meet you at the corner of Pearl and Pine.\N{\rCHT}把你的發現給我送來 羅恩 我在珠寶街和青松道交口等你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:44.40,1:12:45.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Start running. I'll see you in three minutes.\N{\rCHT}跑過來 三分鐘後見{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.60,1:12:48.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What, three minutes? That's a half-mile away! I can't run a half-mile in three...\N{\rCHT}三分鐘? 有一公里呀 我不可能三分鐘跑一公...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.04,1:12:50.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hello?\N{\rCHT}喂?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:52.72,1:12:54.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you folks doing?\N{\rCHT}你們這些人都在幹什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:54.40,1:12:57.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's not O.J.! Get off the street! That's a bomb!\N{\rCHT}他不是明星殺人犯OJ辛普森 快離開街道 那可是炸彈呀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.68,1:12:59.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Bombs explode.\N{\rCHT}炸彈會爆炸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.28,1:13:00.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't want to be near them when they do.\N{\rCHT}爆炸時別靠近{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:00.96,1:13:02.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Frank Ross, reporting from the eye in the sky.\N{\rCHT}我是弗蘭克羅斯 空中攝像正在直播{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:02.60,1:13:05.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He is safely hovering above them.\N{\rCHT}安全地盤旋在他們上空{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.88,1:13:05.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(利·蓋茲和科爾·巴德維爾 他們要去哪?)
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.20,1:13:07.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's a rather distressing scene down here, honestly.\N{\rCHT}說實話 這一鏡頭很令人不安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:08.04,1:13:12.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,New Yorkers flocking to the melee despite repeated police warnings\N{\rCHT}紐約市民紛紛湧上街頭 不顧員警的警告{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:12.12,1:13:16.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,to stay clear of the path of a man with a bomb strapped to his chest.\N{\rCHT}不要靠近這個胸前有炸彈的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:16.56,1:13:18.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Apparently, a lot of people sharing the feelings\N{\rCHT}顯然很多人都很同情{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.96,1:13:20.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of gunman Kyle Budwell this moment.\N{\rCHT}科爾·巴德維爾...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.64,1:13:23.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They are lining the streets, they're cheering him on, as if to say,\N{\rCHT}他們在街道兩旁 給他喝彩 似乎在說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.08,1:13:25.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,"Hey, Ibis, show us the money."\N{\rCHT}"喂 埃比斯 告訴我們錢去哪了"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:37.24,1:13:40.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They're a bunch of crooks! Blow 'em all to hell!\N{\rCHT}他們是一幫混蛋 把他們炸開花{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:40.32,1:13:41.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get off me, man! Come on!\N{\rCHT}放開我 求你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.92,1:13:45.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stay close. Don't let them get a shot at the vest.\N{\rCHT}靠近我 別讓他們對背心開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.08,1:13:49.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now might be a good time to tell you something about that vest then.\N{\rCHT}我想該告訴你 那件背心的事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.36,1:13:54.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There's not actually any Semtex in there. It's just clay. Blocks of clay.\N{\rCHT}根本不是什麼森泰克斯炸藥 只是粘土 粘土磚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.44,1:13:55.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What?\N{\rCHT}什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:13:55.52,1:13:58.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, I wanted to get your attention, not blow up a goddamn building.\N{\rCHT}對 我只是想博取注意力 不是真想炸掉大樓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:00.84,1:14:02.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stand down. Easy.\N{\rCHT}立定 別緊張{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.60,1:14:11.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, they think it's real.\N{\rCHT}他們認為是真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.20,1:14:14.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So whatever you do, don't take your finger off that goddamn trigger.\N{\rCHT}無論如何 你別鬆開關{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:14.20,1:14:16.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're in this together, you dumb shit.\N{\rCHT}我們現在共同進退 你個混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:16.88,1:14:20.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The drama featuring host Lee Gates and Kyle Budwell.\N{\rCHT}事件主角 利·蓋茲和科爾·巴德維爾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:20.80,1:14:23.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wow, this is getting crazy!\N{\rCHT}哇 越來越瘋狂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.72,1:14:24.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at all these people!\N{\rCHT}看看那些人群{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.04,1:14:26.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My phone is blowing up on this.\N{\rCHT}我電話都被這事刷屏了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.20,1:14:29.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If Kyle makes it out of this thing, we got to get him on the show.\N{\rCHT}若科爾被釋放 我們一定要請他來做嘉賓{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.44,1:14:33.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And the next time I have a bad day, I'm gonna come in, "Glitch!"\N{\rCHT}下次我不順心時 我會喊"故障"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:34.80,1:14:38.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Diane, why would Ibis's trading volume suddenly drop 90%?\N{\rCHT}黛安 埃比斯交易量為何驟降90%?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:38.56,1:14:39.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,90%?\N{\rCHT}90%?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.80,1:14:43.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, that's not possible. Ibis's algorithms trade continuously.\N{\rCHT}不可能 埃比斯的演算法是持續交易的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.24,1:14:45.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Somebody would have had to have taken the computers offline.\N{\rCHT}一定是某人切斷電腦連接{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:46.04,1:14:47.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They would have...\N{\rCHT}他們會...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:48.52,1:14:50.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Human fingerprints.\N{\rCHT}人為失誤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:50.72,1:14:52.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt.\N{\rCHT}華特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:52.36,1:14:55.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If Walt took that $800 million away from the algorithm,\N{\rCHT}若華特從演算法拿走了那八億美金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:55.64,1:14:57.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,what did he do with it?\N{\rCHT}他會拿那筆錢做什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:57.24,1:14:59.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have his phone. Shit.\N{\rCHT}我有他的手機 該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:14:59.64,1:15:01.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's deleted all his emails.\N{\rCHT}他把郵件都刪除了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:01.40,1:15:02.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Try texts.\N{\rCHT}試試信息{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.72,1:15:03.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goodloe.\N{\rCHT}古德洛{\r}
