Dialogue: 0,1:17:07.92,1:17:12.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee, are you there? If you can hear me, put your hand in the air.\N{\rCHT}利 你在嗎? 你若能聽到就舉手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:16.04,1:17:19.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. I can see you, but I can't get to you.\N{\rCHT}好 我能看到你 但我過不去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.04,1:17:27.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What am I gonna do?\N{\rCHT}我該怎麼辦?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.92,1:17:31.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We either keep going or we stop. It's up to you.\N{\rCHT}我們可以繼續走 也可以就此結束 你決定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.04,1:17:40.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ESU, forward.\N{\rCHT}緊急事件小組 前進{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:40.96,1:17:43.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,First window we get, we're taking the assailant down.\N{\rCHT}一旦有空隙 我們就擊斃這個混蛋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.84,1:17:44.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Move them back.\N{\rCHT}讓他們退下{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.07,1:17:47.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,{\fs22\fnSimSun}(員警 炸彈分隊)
Dialogue: 0,1:17:47.28,1:17:49.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Stay down.  - Stay behind the car.\N{\rCHT}- 蹲下  - 躲在車後面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:58.28,1:17:59.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Diane, are you still there?\N{\rCHT}黛安 你在聽嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.88,1:18:00.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, I'm here.\N{\rCHT}是的 我在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:00.96,1:18:02.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. We are on Mambo.\N{\rCHT}好 我們在查曼博{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:02.96,1:18:04.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Our van can't get any closer.\N{\rCHT}我們的車不能靠近了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.80,1:18:06.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So keep Walt there.\N{\rCHT}讓華特待在那{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.32,1:18:09.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do not let him run before Lee can get to you.\N{\rCHT}利到達之前 別讓他跑了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:09.28,1:18:10.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, I'll see what I can do.\N{\rCHT}好 我盡力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.76,1:18:11.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right. Get on it, Dave.\N{\rCHT}好的 繼續查 戴夫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.04,1:18:13.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Print out everything you can on this miners' strike.\N{\rCHT}把所有關於罷工的東西都列印出來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.04,1:18:15.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- I'm gonna need that, too.  - Okay.\N{\rCHT}- 我也需要  - 好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.96,1:18:18.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Lee?\N{\rCHT}利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:18.76,1:18:20.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can hear me now.\N{\rCHT}你現在能聽到我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.52,1:18:23.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Which is good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.60,1:18:25.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have a lot to explain,\N{\rCHT}我要解釋很多東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.36,1:18:28.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I need you to listen very carefully for once.\N{\rCHT}你得仔細聽我說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:29.16,1:18:30.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're approaching Federal Hall.\N{\rCHT}我們要去聯邦紀念堂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:31.56,1:18:33.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus. Is that live?\N{\rCHT}天呀 是直播嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.52,1:18:35.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It is now.\N{\rCHT}就是現在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:38.40,1:18:41.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you get all that? And that's before we start digging.\N{\rCHT}你都明白嗎? 那是我們開始調查之前{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.12,1:18:44.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ibis is a pig in a prom dress, Lee.  - Got it.\N{\rCHT}- 埃比斯是個穿著裙子的豬 利  - 明白{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:44.28,1:18:45.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We are trying to find the proof right now.\N{\rCHT}我們現在努力找證據{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.92,1:18:48.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,See if you can get those hacker guys. Find out what they've come up with.\N{\rCHT}看你能否聯繫到那些駭客 看他們能發現什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.76,1:18:51.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, Lee, we're making a pretty big leap here.\N{\rCHT}利 我們現在有很大進展{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:51.24,1:18:54.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So if Walt's gonna hang himself, you're gonna have to hand him that rope.\N{\rCHT}若華特想上吊 你要給他繩子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:54.80,1:18:58.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll just point the camera in your direction, and we'll figure it out together.\N{\rCHT}我會讓攝像機對準你 我們一起來想辦法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.80,1:19:00.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey. Get ready for a show.\N{\rCHT}好 準備表演{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.08,1:19:05.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, these guys are certainly behaving\N{\rCHT}這些人現在的行為好像{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.00,1:19:09.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,like they've got an appointment with the Ibis Clear Capital CEO.\N{\rCHT}他們和埃比斯金融公司首席行政長官 約好了要見面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:09.48,1:19:11.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Which begs the question on everyone's mind,\N{\rCHT}這令大家都很好奇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:11.88,1:19:13.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,where is Walt Camby?\N{\rCHT}華特·坎比在哪?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:13.92,1:19:16.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As a curious crowd assembles outside Federal Hall,\N{\rCHT}聯邦紀念堂外聚集了一群人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.88,1:19:18.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the missing piece of the puzzle...\N{\rCHT}現在缺失的那塊拼圖是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.36,1:19:19.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I trusted you.\N{\rCHT}我是信任你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.64,1:19:22.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, well, I trusted you, too.\N{\rCHT}對 我也信任過你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.04,1:19:25.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So I guess that means we're both wrong.\N{\rCHT}這麼說我們都錯了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:25.72,1:19:28.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What did you do, Diane? I mean, you know me.\N{\rCHT}你幹了什麼 黛安? 你瞭解我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:29.48,1:19:31.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know me better than my wife.\N{\rCHT}你比我妻子更瞭解我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:31.56,1:19:33.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You know me better than anybody.  - I'm not so sure that's true.\N{\rCHT}- 你比任何人都瞭解我  - 我可不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.04,1:19:37.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I have no idea what you think I did.\N{\rCHT}我不知道你以為我做了什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:37.36,1:19:38.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Save it for the cameras, Walt.\N{\rCHT}留著對攝像機說吧 華特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.00,1:19:41.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,An eyewitness in the crowd may just have the answer.\N{\rCHT}或許人群中的目擊者 能告訴我們答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:41.72,1:19:42.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Walt Camby?\N{\rCHT}華特·坎比?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.96,1:19:46.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's inside. He just went up those stairs and through those doors.\N{\rCHT}他就在裡面 他剛從這裡上臺階走進去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.28,1:19:47.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You saw him?  - That's right.\N{\rCHT}- 你看到他了?  - 對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.36,1:19:49.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Guess there's nowhere to run now, huh?\N{\rCHT}我猜無處可逃了吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.40,1:19:52.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This story does seem to be coming to some sort of head down here.\N{\rCHT}看來事件將轉移到這裡{\r}
