Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.88,1:20:21.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Ready for that interview now?  - Hey.\N{\rCHT}- 準備好接受採訪了嗎?  - 喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:21.52,1:20:22.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey.\N{\rCHT}喂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.60,1:20:24.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're just in time for the show.\N{\rCHT}你正好趕上節目播出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:25.68,1:20:26.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How was Geneva?\N{\rCHT}日內瓦如何?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.08,1:20:29.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- It was fine.  - Yeah, I hear it's lovely this time of year.\N{\rCHT}- 不錯  - 是嗎 我聽說今年這個時候挺好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:29.64,1:20:31.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can we get him a chair?\N{\rCHT}能給他椅子嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:31.52,1:20:33.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sam, give him a chair.\N{\rCHT}山姆 給他把椅子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.64,1:20:37.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The Iceland guys just came through with all the facial recognition data.\N{\rCHT}冰島的人剛給我些面部識別資料{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:37.64,1:20:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This footage goes back months.\N{\rCHT}是近幾個月的原始錄影{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:39.60,1:20:41.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Everywhere he's traveled. There's way too much stuff.\N{\rCHT}他去過的所有地方 信息量太大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:41.20,1:20:44.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, well, just focus on the last 48 hours. And cue up the video package.\N{\rCHT}好吧 只看最近48小時 把視頻調出來{\r}
