Dialogue: 0,1:20:47.68,1:20:49.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Wait a second, why does she get to leave?\N{\rCHT}等一下 為什麼她能離開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:49.16,1:20:50.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This might be able to help with your investigation.\N{\rCHT}這個也許能幫助你們調查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.92,1:20:52.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is all her fault.\N{\rCHT}都是她的錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.64,1:20:53.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go ahead, Diane, walk away.\N{\rCHT}你走吧 黛安{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.08,1:20:55.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're the only reason we're stuck here with this psycho.\N{\rCHT}都是因為你 我們才和這個瘋子困在一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:55.84,1:20:58.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You wanted transparency, Walt? Well, here's your chance.\N{\rCHT}你想要公開嗎 華特? 你的機會來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:20:58.36,1:20:59.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's go.\N{\rCHT}走吧{\r}
