Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.20,1:21:19.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, Walt, now that we have you here in person,\N{\rCHT}華特 既然你親自到場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.80,1:21:22.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we can finally ask the $800 million question.\N{\rCHT}我們終於可以問問那八億美金的事了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:23.36,1:21:24.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What happened at Ibis, Walt?\N{\rCHT}埃比斯出了什麼事 華特?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.68,1:21:30.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As we've been saying since day one, this was an isolated computer glitch.\N{\rCHT}我們從第一天就開始說 那是孤立電腦故障事件{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:30.76,1:21:32.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Goddamn it!\N{\rCHT}該死{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.80,1:21:34.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Glitch!  - He doesn't really like that word.\N{\rCHT}- 故障  - 他不喜歡那個詞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.64,1:21:36.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I fuckin' hate that word!\N{\rCHT}我他媽恨死這個詞了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.28,1:21:37.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not the glitch.\N{\rCHT}不是故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:37.60,1:21:39.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Cue up video one.  - I fucking hate that word.\N{\rCHT}- 放視頻一  - 我他媽討厭這個詞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:39.48,1:21:41.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And then line the rest of 'em up on my mark.\N{\rCHT}然後聽我指示依次放其他視頻{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:41.84,1:21:45.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You tried to convince us it's all too complicated for us to understand.\N{\rCHT}你想叫我們相信 事情太複雜我們不會理解的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:45.92,1:21:47.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But it's not that complicated at all, is it?\N{\rCHT}但根本沒那麼複雜吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.64,1:21:51.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's actually the oldest story in the book. Fraud.\N{\rCHT}其實就是老把戲 詐騙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:51.80,1:21:55.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You took money out of your fund and you invested it here.\N{\rCHT}你從你的基金拿錢出來 投資到這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:55.16,1:21:56.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go.\N{\rCHT}放{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:21:57.00,1:22:00.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right here in platinum mines in South Africa. Does that sound familiar?\N{\rCHT}就在南非的鉑金礦 聽著耳熟嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.36,1:22:03.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't have our portfolio in front of me. I can't exactly...\N{\rCHT}我現在沒有我們的投資組合 我無法準確地...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.88,1:22:07.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You really need your portfolio to know where you put $800 million?\N{\rCHT}你真需要看投資組合檔案 才知道那八億去哪了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.60,1:22:09.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't put that much money anywhere.\N{\rCHT}那錢我哪都沒放{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.60,1:22:10.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The algorithms control our day-to-day...\N{\rCHT}是演算法控制日常的...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:10.96,1:22:14.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But that's not how high-frequency trading is supposed to work, is it?\N{\rCHT}但高頻率交易不該這樣做吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:14.16,1:22:16.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They don't just put that much money in one place\N{\rCHT}他們不會把這麼多錢放在一個地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:16.36,1:22:18.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and just leave it there, do they?\N{\rCHT}然後就不管了吧?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.40,1:22:21.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It wasn't the algos pullin' the strings, it was you.\N{\rCHT}不是演算法的責任 是你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:22.04,1:22:26.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The miners' union strike here outside Johannesburg is on its second week.\N{\rCHT}約翰尼斯堡的礦工工會罷工進入第二周{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:26.20,1:22:29.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You. You bought and paid for a two-week strike.\N{\rCHT}你 是你出錢進行的兩周罷工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.48,1:22:31.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Come on. This is ridiculous.\N{\rCHT}得了吧 這太荒唐了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.36,1:22:32.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go.\N{\rCHT}放{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:32.76,1:22:35.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The strike had caused the mining company's stock to drop.\N{\rCHT}罷工導致礦公司股票價格下跌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:35.88,1:22:38.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You buy low, you get the strike to stop, you sell high.\N{\rCHT}你低價買進 讓罷工停止 然後就高價賣出{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:39.04,1:22:40.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the plan.\N{\rCHT}這就是你的計畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.48,1:22:43.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You make one big bribe to the right guy, line your own pockets,\N{\rCHT}你找了個合適的人賄賂 錢進自己口袋{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:43.56,1:22:44.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and no one'll be the wiser.\N{\rCHT}沒人比你更聰明{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:44.80,1:22:48.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're making accusations that have no basis in reality.\N{\rCHT}你這是毫無根據的指責{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.24,1:22:49.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Video three on my mark.\N{\rCHT}準備視頻三{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:49.40,1:22:51.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- All right, all right, all right. One...  - Get it together.\N{\rCHT}- 好的 好的 等...  - 快點兒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:51.12,1:22:52.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Okay, it's there. Got it.  - It's defamation, okay?\N{\rCHT}- 好了 行了  - 這是誹謗 好嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.44,1:22:53.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And there are laws about that.\N{\rCHT}誹謗是犯法的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:53.72,1:22:55.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go on, Walt. Tell me about all the laws I'm breaking.\N{\rCHT}繼續 華特 說我犯了什麼法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:55.72,1:22:57.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Ready when you are, Lee. On your mark.\N{\rCHT}準備好了 利 等你的指示{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:57.40,1:22:58.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, I'll give you this.\N{\rCHT}我給你看看這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:22:58.56,1:23:02.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There really was a glitch in your system. It just wasn't the computer.\N{\rCHT}你的系統裡的確出了故障 但不是電腦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:02.16,1:23:03.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It was this guy. Moshe Mambo.\N{\rCHT}是這個人 摩西·曼博{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.88,1:23:05.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We must say no!\N{\rCHT}我們必須決絕{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.80,1:23:10.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We must say no to their businesses! We must say no to their bribes!\N{\rCHT}我們必須拒絕他們的交易 我們必須拒絕他們的賄賂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.76,1:23:13.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You tried to bribe the one guy that couldn't be bought.\N{\rCHT}你想賄賂這個人 但他不買帳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:13.80,1:23:16.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All they care about is money!\N{\rCHT}他們只在乎錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:17.08,1:23:21.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,If it takes two years, if it takes 20 years,\N{\rCHT}就算需要兩年 就算20年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.80,1:23:26.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we will stay here and strike until our voices are heard.\N{\rCHT}我們都會繼續罷工 直到我們受到關注{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.20,1:23:27.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Pause.\N{\rCHT}暫停{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.16,1:23:31.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There. Right there. That's your glitch.\N{\rCHT}就這裡 這是你說的故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.68,1:23:34.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Because that's what sent the mining company's stock plummeting,\N{\rCHT}因為這導致了礦公司的股票暴跌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:34.76,1:23:37.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,which sent your secret $800 million investment\N{\rCHT}讓你的八個億投資{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.40,1:23:38.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,right into the toilet.\N{\rCHT}付諸流水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.84,1:23:41.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Want me to keep goin'?\N{\rCHT}還要我繼續嗎?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:42.12,1:23:44.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Patty. You gotta see this.  - You made people a lot of money, Walt.\N{\rCHT}- 帕蒂 你得看看這個  - 你讓大家賺了很多錢 華特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:44.76,1:23:48.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You just needed to wreck industries and destroy economies all over the world to do it.\N{\rCHT}你只需要毀了產業和世界各地的經濟...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:48.16,1:23:51.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay. Get that ready right now. Lee?\N{\rCHT}好 馬上準備好 利?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:51.80,1:23:53.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're gonna say everything I say.\N{\rCHT}你重複我說的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:53.20,1:23:54.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is insane.\N{\rCHT}這太瘋狂了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.60,1:23:57.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I don't know the first thing about some South African workers' strike.\N{\rCHT}我不知道什麼南非工人罷工{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:23:57.80,1:24:00.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've never even heard of this Mambo.\N{\rCHT}我都沒聽過曼博這個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.32,1:24:02.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Really? Never?  - Really? Never?\N{\rCHT}- 真的? 從沒聽過?  - 真的? 從沒聽過?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.40,1:24:04.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, what were you two arguing about this morning?\N{\rCHT}那你們兩個今天上午在吵什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.20,1:24:06.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then what were you two arguing about this morning\N{\rCHT}那你們兩個今天上午在吵什麼?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:07.08,1:24:09.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,at 8:02 a.m., local time?\N{\rCHT}在當地時間8點02分?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:10.08,1:24:12.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Or maybe they're speaking Swahili in Geneva these days.\N{\rCHT}或者也許日內瓦如今 開始說斯瓦希裡語了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:12.48,1:24:15.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They don't speak Swahili in South Africa, either.\N{\rCHT}南非也不說斯瓦希裡語{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.64,1:24:19.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And this wasn't the first time you did it, either.\N{\rCHT}你這不是第一次了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.44,1:24:22.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This was just the first time it didn't work out.\N{\rCHT}只不過是第一次不奏效而已{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:23.56,1:24:25.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You feel that, Walt?\N{\rCHT}你感覺到了嗎 華特?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:25.68,1:24:29.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That sticky heat risin' up the back of your neck?\N{\rCHT}脖梗子發熱?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.64,1:24:32.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That flop sweat?\N{\rCHT}出汗了?{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:33.64,1:24:35.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's fear.\N{\rCHT}這就是恐懼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:35.48,1:24:37.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Greed you're already acquainted with.\N{\rCHT}你熟悉的貪婪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:38.40,1:24:42.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's all a great story, Lee. I'm actually sorry the real one's so boring.\N{\rCHT}這故事真好 利 我真的很抱歉事實卻很無聊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:42.76,1:24:44.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But the truth is, our computational systems are far too...\N{\rCHT}事實是 我們的計算系統至今為止...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:44.96,1:24:46.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, forget it. Just shoot him.\N{\rCHT}別管了 一槍斃了他{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:46.48,1:24:48.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Actually, I got a better idea.\N{\rCHT}事實上我有個更好的點子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:48.68,1:24:50.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Up. Up, up, up.\N{\rCHT}站起來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:51.24,1:24:53.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Take the vest off. Put it on him.\N{\rCHT}把背心脫了 給他穿上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:53.84,1:24:54.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah? Go ahead.\N{\rCHT}行嗎? 動手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:54.96,1:24:56.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hold on. That's just gonna make things worse.\N{\rCHT}等等 這只會令事情更糟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:56.40,1:24:58.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I already told you, back off.\N{\rCHT}我說過了 你後退{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:58.52,1:24:59.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fuckin' cops.\N{\rCHT}該死的員警{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:24:59.92,1:25:01.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Lenny.  - All right.\N{\rCHT}- 蘭尼  - 好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:01.84,1:25:03.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- Now? Okay.  - Just right here.\N{\rCHT}- 現在? 好  - 站這{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:03.80,1:25:06.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Listen, I'm gonna do you a solid. And trust me on this.\N{\rCHT}聽著 我都按你說的做 你相信我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:06.48,1:25:08.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't turn your back on anybody.\N{\rCHT}別背對著任何人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:12.16,1:25:13.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're a thief, Walt.\N{\rCHT}你是小偷 華特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.36,1:25:15.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And a crook.\N{\rCHT}是騙子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.20,1:25:16.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And I want to hear you admit it.\N{\rCHT}我要聽你承認{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:16.88,1:25:17.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I didn't steal a dime,\N{\rCHT}我一分錢都沒偷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:18.08,1:25:19.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- and we didn't do anything illegal.  - Bullshit!\N{\rCHT}- 我們沒做任何犯法的事  - 胡說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.64,1:25:21.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You manipulated stock prices.  - You don't care what I'm gonna say.\N{\rCHT}- 你操縱股票價格  - 你不在乎我要說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.84,1:25:22.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You bribed people.  - You need someone to blame.\N{\rCHT}- 你賄賂  - 你要找人怪罪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.04,1:25:24.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- You broke the law.  - You've already decided it's gonna be me.\N{\rCHT}- 你犯了法  - 你已經決定是我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:24.96,1:25:28.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What law? Name one law you can prove I broke.\N{\rCHT}什麼法? 說一條你能證明我違犯了的法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:28.60,1:25:30.40,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, don't look at him. He can't prove it, either.\N{\rCHT}不 別看著他 他也證明不了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:30.52,1:25:33.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is just business. And this is how business is done.\N{\rCHT}這是買賣而已 買賣就是這樣做的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.28,1:25:35.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,- That doesn't make it right.  - Please.\N{\rCHT}- 這沒道理  - 拜託{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:36.00,1:25:37.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell that to the Chinese.\N{\rCHT}跟中國人說去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.68,1:25:39.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Tell that to the Russians. 'Cause if it's not us, it's gonna be them.\N{\rCHT}跟俄國人說去 因為若不是我們 就是他們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.04,1:25:41.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hell, it already is.\N{\rCHT}已經如此了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:41.72,1:25:43.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You see, that's the irony about all this.\N{\rCHT}你看 就是這麼諷刺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:43.76,1:25:45.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You only came after me 'cause I lost you money.\N{\rCHT}你只知道找我算帳 因為我讓你吃虧了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:45.96,1:25:48.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nobody was asking questions when everybody was makin' a profit.\N{\rCHT}大家賺錢的時候就沒人提問{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.64,1:25:51.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You just gobbled up every dollar of stock you could afford.\N{\rCHT}只會投入每一分能負擔的錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.04,1:25:54.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,As long as we kept paying you 18% ROI every year,\N{\rCHT}只要我們保持每年18%的回報率{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.00,1:25:57.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,then you could keep bragging to your friends about what a genius you are.\N{\rCHT}你們就會向朋友們炫耀自己是多麼天才{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.56,1:25:59.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, hey, you're not a genius,\N{\rCHT}但你不是天才{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:25:59.52,1:26:00.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you're a stockholder.\N{\rCHT}你是個投資者而已{\r}
